estyle%20standpoint%2C%20what%20do%20you%20value%3F%20If%20you're%20planning%20before%20you%20have%20a%20family%2C%20how%20would%20kids%20impact%20the%20picture%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAllocca%20said%20she%20frequently%20gets%20questions%20about%20how%20major%20life%20decisions%20%E2%80%94%20like%20having%20children%20%E2%80%94%20affect%20someone's%20financial%20independence%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can't%20give%20a%20straight%20answer%20because%20I%20don't%20know%20your%20life%20%E2%80%94%20how%20many%20kids%20you%20want%2C%20what%20kind%20of%20lifestyle%20you're%20aiming%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThose%20things%20have%20to%20be%20factored%20into%20the%20plan.%20I%20think%20this%20book%20does%20a%20good%20job%20of%20helping%20you%20think%20through%20it%20in%20a%20tactical%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226ccfe634-2748-4090-88b1-b5cdd6beb4e5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3D30284f0c0a34917577aef78b3f479ffb0b4ce17c295fbe3fc5ae183c658523ac%26postID%3D69ab194472b302110f46545e%26postSlug%3Dtop-money-book-recommendations-retire-early-financial-independence-fire-2026-3%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.barnesandnoble.com%252Fw%252Fbig-magic-elizabeth-gilbert%252F1121030101%253Fean%253D9781594634727%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBig%20Magic%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3B%20by%20Elizabeth%20Gilbert%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Rose%20Han%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-who-hit-fire-shares-the-realities-of-early-retirement-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eearly%20retirement%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20once%20the%20ultimate%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%2032%2C%20I%20basically%20achieved%20a%20version%20of%20FIRE%20%E2%80%94%20living%20in%20my%20camper%20van%20and%20having%20freedom%20%E2%