0I%20never%20earned%20a%20degree.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20two%20years%2C%20I%20bought%20a%20condo%20using%20some%20of%20the%20money%20I%20got%20from%20selling%20my%20home%20in%20Wisconsin%20after%20my%20divorce.%20We%20didn't%20have%20everything%2C%20but%20we%20were%20comfortable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tried%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-smart-people-do-get-out-of-debt-soon-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eavoid%20debt%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20it%20was%20too%20overwhelming%20for%20me.%20I%20was%20content%20with%20resale%20shops.%20The%20one%20thing%20I%20was%20willing%20to%20pay%20for%20was%20nice%20cars%2C%20but%20I%20always%20got%20good%20deals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20kids%20lived%20with%20me%20after%20high%20school%2C%20they%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-back-home-was-the-smartest-financial-move-i-made-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epaid%20rent%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20wasn't%20a%20lot%2C%20and%20it%20depended%20on%20what%20they%20could%20afford%2C%20but%20I%20figured%20they%20had%20to%20learn%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ce87b2ea-af90-4a68-aaa9-0e990bc08de0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20family%20is%20scattered%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20oldest%20son%2C%20Todd%2C%20lives%20in%20Minnesota%20with%20two%20kids.%20My%20daughter%2C%20Dawn%2C%20lives%20in%20Arizona%20in%20my%20other%20house%2C%20and%20she%20has%20two%20kids.%20One%20of%20them%2C%20Paul%2C%20lives%20in%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20and%20the%20other%2C%20Christie%2C%20moved%20in%20with%20me%20at%2016%20when%20she%20had%20Jaidden%2C%20her%20first%20child.%20She%20had%20Jeremiah%20six%20years%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaul%20stayed%20with%20me%20until%20he%20was%2024.%20Christie%20came%20home%20to%20me%20from%20the%20hospital%20with%20her%20baby.%20Both%20went%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-job-back-school-new-career-masters-40s-start-again-2026-2%