%20labor%20issue%20inside%20manufacturing%20plants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Oregon-based%20startup%20has%20so%20far%20deployed%20its%20humanoid%20robot%2C%20Digit%2C%20at%20Amazon%2C%20Schaeffler%20Group%2C%20and%20GXO%2C%20a%20logistics%20company.%20The%20startup%20announced%20in%20February%20that%20a%20few%20Digit%20robots%20would%20be%20deployed%20in%20Toyota's%20massive%20manufacturing%20plant%20in%20Canada%2C%20marking%20yet%20another%20automaker%20betting%20on%20bipedal%20bots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDaniel%20Diez%2C%20Agility's%20chief%20business%20officer%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20there's%20a%20common%20thread%20at%20the%20companies%20he%20visits%20around%20the%20world.%20In%20Germany%2C%20Korea%2C%20Japan%2C%20or%20the%20US%2C%20manufacturers%20just%20don't%20have%20enough%20people%20who%20want%20to%20work%20mundane%2C%20repetitive%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Headshot%20of%20Daniel%20Diez%2C%20chief%20business%20officer%20of%20Agility%20Robotics%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ab7345fd4fbd083f29b77a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDaniel%20Diez%2C%20Agility%20Robotics'%20chief%20business%20officer%2C%20said%20there's%20a%20labor%20gap%20in%20manufacturing%20that%20will%20require%20automation.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Agility%20Robotics%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20same%20exact%20issue%3A%20Labor%20gaps%20in%20these%20highly%20repetitive%20physical%20tasks%2C%26quot%3B%20Diez%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20simply%20can't%20find%20the%20people%20to%20do%20this%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20shortage%20of%20manufacturing%20roles.%20According%20to%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Labor%20Statistics%2C%20there%20are%20more%20than%20400%2C000%20job%20openings%20in%20the%20sector%20in%20the%20US%20as%20of%20December%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20vacancies%2C%20talent%20retention%20remains%20a%20top%20concern%20for%20manufacturers%2C%20according%20to%20a%202024%20survey%20of%20more%20than%20200%20companies%20conducted%20by%20The%20Manufacturing%20Institute%20and%20Deloitte.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDiez%20said%20there%20are%20%26quot%3Bcompounding%20effects%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20so-called%20labor%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20significant%20share%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-are-struggling-to-fill-existing-manufacturing-positions-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emanufacturing%20workforce%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%2055%20and%20over%2C%20he%20said%2C%20meaning%20they're%20approaching%20retirement.%20BLS's%20Current%20Population%20Survey%20clocks%20the%20number%20at%20a%20little%20over%2025%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdd%20to%20that%20the%20Trump%20Administration's%20push%20to%20bring%20onshore%20manufacturing%20back%2C%20which%20Diez%20said%20will%20only%20create%20more%20jobs%20and%20a%20greater%20need%20for%20automation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20re-shoring%20of%20manufacturing%20in%20the%20US%20is%20going%20to%20only%20occur%20through%20a%20combination%20of%20human%20employment%20and%20automation%20technology%2C%20like%20humans%20and%20robotics%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAutomakers%20are%20notably%20bracing%20for%20this%20shifting%20tide.%20Tesla%2C%20Volkswagen%2C%20Ford%2C%20Mercedes-Benz%2C%20and%20Hyundai%2C%20among%20others%2C%20have%20made%20significant%20investments%20in%20humanoid%20robots%20with%20the%20prospect%20that%20they'll%20work%20the%20assembly%20lines%20in%20the%20near%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20humanoid%20robot%20stands%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ab6e72d3e2f1aef36a2e95%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAtlas%2C%20Boston%20Dynamics'%20humanoid%20robot%2C%20will%20be%20deployed%20in%20Hyundai's%20factory%20in%202028.%3Cp%3ELloyd%20