F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-testing-humanoid-robots-digit-warehouses-agility-robotics-boston-dynamics-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebipedal%20form%20factor%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20easier%20integration%20into%20existing%20or%20older%20factories%2C%20Diez%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20this%20moment%20in%20time%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20an%20ideal%20solution%20for%20brownfield%20facilities%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20underutilized%20industrial%20facilities%20that%20tend%20to%20have%20a%20baked-in%20layout.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20with%20humanoids%2C%20manufacturers%20can%20automate%20their%20properties%20without%20making%20significant%20changes%20to%20the%20factory%20layout%20and%20workflow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDiez%20said%20that%20any%20industry%20with%20highly%20repetitive%20tasks%20is%20ripe%20for%20the%20adoption%20of%20humanoid%20robots.%20The%20industries%20Agility%20Robotics%20is%20seeing%20with%20the%20most%20%26quot%3Binbound%26quot%3B%20requests%20are%20coming%20from%20warehouse%20logistics%2C%20e-commerce%20fulfillment%2C%20automotive%2C%20and%20pharmaceutical%20manufacturing%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20having%20to%20convince%20people%20that%20this%20is%20a%20technology%20need%2C%26quot%3B%20Diez%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20more%20than%20enough%20hand-raisers%20who%20are%20coming%20to%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fagility-robotics-humanoid-robots-labor-shortage-aging-workforce-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772959441000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ab860bd3e2f1aef36a2f08%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fagility-robotics-humanoid-robots-labor-shortage-aging-workforce-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Agility%20Robotics%20is%20building%20humanoid%20bots%20to%20address%20a%20labor%20gap%20in%20the%20manufacturing%20industry%2C%20which%20is%20seeing%20vacancies%20and%20an%20aging%20workforce.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fagility-robotics-humanoid-robots-labor-shortage-aging-workforce-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20survival%20training%20that%20kicks%20in%20after%20an%20American%20pilot%20is%20shot%20down%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222942%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20US%20Air%20Force%20F-15%20jets%20were%20shot%20down%20in%20a%20friendly%20fire%20incident%20over%20Kuwait%20on%20Sunday.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a8a194fd4fbd083f298971%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221324%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThree%20US%20Air%20Force%20F-15%20jets%20were%20shot%20down%20in%20a%20friendly%20fire%20incident%20over%20Kuwait%20on%20Sunday.%3Cp%3ESenior%20Airman%20Jonah%20Bliss%2FUS%20Air%20Force%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EVideos%20online%20show%20US%20F-15%20pilots'%20first%20apparent%20moments%20on%20the%20ground%20after%20ejecting%20Sunday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEven%20a%20successful%20ejection%20often%20leaves%20pilots%20injured%20and%20disoriented.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMilitary%20aircrews%20train%20for%20what%20happens%20if%20their%20aircraft%20goes%20down%20behind%20enemy%20lines.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESix%20American%20airmen%20were%20forced%20to%20eject%20Sunday%20after%20three%20F-15E%20Strike%20Eagles%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-aircraft-losses-iran-israel-kuwait-several-warplanes-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshot%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20what%20US%20Central%20Command%20described%20as%20a%20friendly%20fire%20incident.%20Videos%20of%20one%20jet%20spiraling%20to%20the%20ground%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D1562224778183963%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewent%20viral%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rare%20friendly-fire%20shootdown%20shows%20why%20pilot%20survival%20training%20is%20as%20critical%20as%20combat%20skill%20%E2%80%94%20and%20how%20violently%20things%20can%20go%20wrong%20even%20in%20%26quot%3Bfriendly%26quot%3B%20airspace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ff873a9c-d147-438b-8ab0-6ad0e2fe91bc%5C%22%3EEjection%20Training%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMilitary%20aviators%20regularly%20undergo%20refresher%20training%20on%20surviving%20aircraft%20emergencies%2C%20from%20what%20to%20do%20when%20oxygen%20levels%20drop%20dangerously%20low%20to%20escaping%20a%20downed%20aircraft%20at%20sea%2C%20said%20Vincent%20Aiello%2C%20a%20retired%20Navy%20fighter%20pilot%20and%20former%20TOPGUN%20instructor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFlying%20a%20high-performance%20fighter%20jet%20is%20a%20full-contact%20sport%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20difficult%20on%20your%20body.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESafe%20ejection%20preparation%20begins%20with%20body%20positioning.%20Because%20an%20ejection%20seat%20goes%20through%20what%20Aiello%20described%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bcontrolled%20explosion%2C%26quot%3B%20even%20small%20deviations%20can%20cause%20severe%20injury.%20The%20seat%20rockets%20a%20pilot%20out%20of%20the%20cockpit%20in%20a%20fraction%20of%20a%20second%2C%20generating%20forces%20strong%20enough%20to%20compress%20the%20spine%20and%20leave%20lasting%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20improper%20position%20of%20an%20aviator's%20body%20can%20be%20fatal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221968%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Airmen%20learn%20to%20properly%20adjust%20ejection%20seats%20in%20a%20course%20to%20ensure%20they're%20ready%20to%20use%20in%20an%20emergency.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ab1134fd4fbd083f29ac24%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221312%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAirmen%20learn%20to%20properly%20adjust%20ejection%20seats%20in%20a%20course%20to%20ensure%20they're%20ready%20to%20use%20in%20an%20emergency.%3Cp%3E2nd%20Lt.%20Lauren%20Niemi%2FUS%20Air%20Force%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAiello%20recalled%20being%20in%20an%20ejection%20simulator%20in%20one%20of%20his%20early%20training%20sessions%20%E2%80%94%20sensors%20detected%20if%20an%20elbow%20or%20foot%20was%20even%20a%20hair%20out%20of%20position%2C%20mistakes%20that%20in%20a%20real%20scenario%20could%20prove%20extremely%20harmful%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20just%20the%20explosion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20%E2%80%94%20a%20pilot%20is%20%26quot%3Briding%20this%20blast%20wave%26quot%3B%20and%20can%20be%20thrown%20into%20the%20aircraft's%20slipstream%2C%20which%20may%20be%20moving%20at%20hundreds%20of%20miles%20per%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20ejection%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dx1IhlU1qFN4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emulti-step%20process%3C%2Fa%3E.%20After%20the%20ejection%20handle%20is%20pulled%2C%20the%20cockpit%20canopy%20blasts%20off%20and%20then%20a%20rocket%20motor%20under%20the%20aviator's%20seat%20fires%20to%20carry%20them%20safely%20away%20from%20the%20aircraft%20before%20releasing%20a%20parachute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20is%20intense%20and%20disorienting%2C%20Aiello%20explained%2C%20and%20is%20made%20even%20more%20difficult%20with%20military%20parachutes%20that%20are%20designed%20more%20for%20survivability%20than%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efor%20easy%20maneuverability%20and%20soft%20landings%2C%20like%20sport%20parachutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20almost%20guaranteed%20to%20be%20injured%2C%20but%20you%20should%20be%20alive%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that's%20the%20point%2C%20you%20don't%20go%20down%20with%20the%20ship.%20You%20get%20out%2C%20albeit%20violently%2C%20but%20you're%20alive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20aircrew%20student%20was%20dragged%20through%20the%20water%20during%20a%202005%20training.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ab12effd4fbd083f29ac5f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20aircrew%20student%20was%20dragged%20through%20the%20water%20during%20a%202005%20training.%3Cp%3EPO2%20Scott%20Taylor%2FUS%20Navy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f1f6bf53-0617-47fd-8880-383db25e18e1%5C%22%3ESERE%20Training%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20out%20of%20the%20jet%20is%20only%20the%20first%20hurdle%20if%20a%20pilot%20goes%20down%20in%20unfriendly%20territory%20%E2%80%94%20what%20happens%20in%20the%20minutes%20and%20hours%20immediately%20after%20landing%20can%20determine%20whether%20a%20pilot%20makes%20it%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20US%20military%20aviators%20and%20aircrew%20undergo%20SERE%20training%20%E2%80%94%20short%20for%20%26quot%3BSurvive%2C%20Evade%2C%20Resist%2C%20Escape.%26quot%3B%20The%20program%2C%20also%20required%20for%20personnel%20assigned%20to%20special%20operations%20units%20and%20others%2C%20prepares%20service%20members%20for%20isolation%20and%20potential%20captivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20the%20training%20was%20shaped%20by%20lessons%20from%20the%20Korean%20and%20Vietnam%20wars%2C%20when%20thousands%20of%20American%20service%20members%2C%20including%20pilots%20and%20aircrew%2C%20were%20taken%20prisoner%20and%20subjected%20to%20torture%20and%20inhumane%20conditions.%20Back%20then%2C%20there%20was%20little%20formal%20preparation%20for%20what%20troops%20might%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20multiple%20SERE%20schools%20train%20military%20personnel%20how%20to%20survive%20being%20captured%20by%20an%20enemy%20and%20follow%20a%20similar%20concept%20%E2%80%94%20after%20classroom%20instruction%2C%20students%20spend%20several%20days%20living%20off%20the%20land%20before%20attempting%20to%20evade%20simulated%20enemy%20forces.%20They%20then%20undergo%20a%20%26quot%3Bcapture%26quot%3B%20and%20experience%20a%20prisoner-of-war%20camp%20environment%2C%20where%20they%20are%20tested%20through%20interrogations%20and%20propaganda%20scenarios.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20that%20means%20realistic%20stress%20for%20troops%20who%20must%20stick%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bcode%20of%20conduct%26quot%3B%20for%20POWs%2C%20a%20set%20of%20rules%20meant%20to%20guide%20captured%20personnel%20through%20interrogations%20and%20torture%2C%20and%20to%20resist%20divulging%20sensitive%20information.%20Service%20members%20must%20also%20demonstrate%20their%20ability%20to%20maintain%20discipline%20and%20morale%20under%20sustained%20psychological%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pilots%20train%20for%20how%20to%20survive%20capture%20by%20a%20repressive%20regime%20in%20the%20Survival%2C%20Evasion%2C%20Resistance%20and%20Escape%20course.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ab1487fd4fbd083f29ac9d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221331%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPilots%20train%20for%20how%20to%20survive%20capture%20by%20a%20repressive%20regime%20in%20the%20Survival%2C%20Evasion%2C%20Resistance%20and%20Escape%20course.%3Cp%3ESenior%20Airman%20Robert%20Nichols%2FUS%20Air%20Force%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20conflict%20against%20a%20nation%20with%20advanced%20air%20defenses%2C%20the%20odds%20of%20ejecting%20into%20hostile%20territory%20rise%20sharply%2C%20making%20the%20training%20critical.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhether%20you're%20in%20the%20jungle%2C%20the%20Arctic%2C%20or%20the%20desert%2C%20you're%20learning%20a%20mindset%2C%26quot%3B%20explained%20James%20Reeman%2C%20a%20retired%20Air%20National%20Guard%20F-16%20pilot.%20%26quot%3BHow%20am%20I%20going%20to%20be%20mentally%20prepared%20if%20things%20go%20wrong%3F%26quot%3B%20It's%20an%20extreme%20example%20of%20being%20tested%20to%20personal%20limits%2C%20with%20sleep%20deprivation%20and%20simulated%20interrogations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20experience%20of%20evading%20and%20resisting%20in%20small%20teams%20creates%20strong%20bonds%2C%20he%20said%2C%20and%20leaves%20little%20room%20for%20any%20big%20egos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20at%20your%20wits%20end%2C%20and%20they%20do%20a%20really%20good%20job%20of%20making%20you%20think%20it's%20real%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Boot%20Camp%3A%20How%20The%20Air%20Force%20Trains%20For%20Crashes%20in%20Enemy%20Territory%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.jwplayer.com%2Fplayers%2FmFptnuEu-puACk8ZV.html%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20last%20thing%20you%20expect%20is%20to%20get%20shot%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20John%20Waters%2C%20who%20previously%20flew%20with%20the%20Air%20Force's%20F-16%20Viper%20Demonstration%20Team%2C%20especially%20by%20friends.%20But%20the%20unexpected%20can't%20be%20where%20everything%20falls%20apart.%20That's%20where%20pilots%20and%20aircrews%20lean%20hardest%20on%20their%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20military%20invests%20heavily%20in%20keeping%20pilots%20alive%2C%20not%20just%20because%20of%20the%20human%20cost.%20Experienced%20aviators%20are%20among%20its%20most%20expensive%20and%20difficult%20assets%20to%20replace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222990%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22SERE%20trains%20pilots%20and%20aircrew%20on%20how%20to%20be%20ready%20in%20case%20they%20need%20to%20eject.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ab15ced3e2f1aef36a2429%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221989%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESERE%20trains%20pilots%20and%20aircrew%20on%20how%20to%20be%20ready%20in%20case%20they%20need%20to%20eject.%3Cp%3ESenior%20Airman%20Tiffany%20Del%20Oso%2FUS%20Air%20Force%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESERE%20training%20places%20aviators%20in%20high-stress%20environments%20specifically%20to%20test%20whether%20they%20can%20regain%20composure%20quickly%20and%20manage%20unpredictable%20interactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20today's%20conflicts%2C%20the%20first%20people%20a%20downed%20pilot%20meets%20may%20be%20civilians%20with%20smartphones%2C%20not%20soldiers%2C%20adding%20a%20new%20layer%20of%20unpredictability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20friendly%20fire%20incident%20involving%20the%20F-15s%2C%20video%20footage%20began%20circulating%20online%20showing%20what%20was%20said%20to%20be%20American%20pilots%20encountering%20locals%20in%20Kuwait.%20Waters%20pointed%20to%20the%20footage%20of%20a%20pilot%20raising%20their%20hands%20as%20the%20locals%20approached%20as%20de-escalation%20under%20pressure.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPilots%20fly%20with%20sidearms%20in%20case%20they%20find%20themselves%20in%20an%20emergency%20on%20the%20ground%E2%80%94%20but%20knowing%20when%20to%20engage%20and%20when%20not%20to%20is%20critical.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20obviously%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20ways%20this%20could%20have%20ended%2C%26quot%3B%20Waters%20said%2C%20referring%20broadly%20to%20the%20friendly%20fire%20incident.%20However%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20could%20have%20been%20much%20worse%20if%20this%20had%20happened%20over%20territory%20where%20people%20weren't%20friendly%2C%20or%20where%20there%20wasn't%20a%20friendly%20government.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-survival-training-that-kicks-in-after-pilot-is-down-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772959381000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ab15dad3e2f1aef36a242f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22ori