an%20at%20a%20job%20interview%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a9aad1d3e2f1aef36a0af0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223744%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20a%20cooling%20job%20market%2C%20prestige%20is%20helping%20some%20elite%20college%20graduates%20stand%20out.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20hiring%20slowdown%20has%20made%20it%20harder%20for%20even%20elite%20college%20graduates%20to%20land%20jobs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20as%20employers%20grow%20more%20selective%2C%20the%20prestige%20of%20an%20Ivy%20League%20degree%20can%20still%20pay%20off.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20employers%20have%20narrowed%20their%20recruiting%20to%20a%20select%20group%20of%20schools.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20few%20years%2C%20a%20hot%20job%20market%20cast%20doubt%20on%20the%20need%20for%20an%20elite%20college%20diploma.%20In%20a%20tough%20job%20market%2C%20that%20trend%20is%20reversing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMatt%20Stabile%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20recruitment%20firm%20Stabile%20Search%2C%20which%20focuses%20on%20AI%20roles%20in%20quantitative%20finance%20in%20the%20New%20York%20City%20area%2C%20said%20he's%20observed%20a%20shift%20in%20recruiting%20in%20recent%20years%3A%20graduates%20from%20top%20universities%20are%20back%20in%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20really%20been%20a%20return%20to%20a%20demand%20for%20people%20coming%20from%20top%20academic%20backgrounds%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20better%20or%20worse%2C%20these%20top%20companies%20use%20this%20metric%20as%20a%20way%20to%20weed%20out%20the%20thousands%20of%20people%20that%20apply%20to%20them%20every%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20that%20companies%20were%20ever%20ignoring%20graduates%20from%20top-tier%20universities%2C%20Stabile%20said.%20A%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20when%20firms%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgreat-resignation-what-to-know-who-is-quitting-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escrambling%20to%20fill%20roles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20many%20broadened%20their%20hiring%20standards.%20Now%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjob-market-find-work-employment-hiring-slowdown-careers-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethat%20hiring%20has%20slowed%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20said%2C%20they%20can%20afford%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bchoosier%26quot%3B%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FhQQwM%2F2%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Nonfarm%20payrolls%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22448%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EA%202025%20survey%20of%20more%20than%20150%20employers%20found%20that%2026%25%20said%20they%20were%20recruiting%20exclusively%20from%20a%20select%20group%20of%20schools%2C%20up%20from%2017%25%20in%202022%2C%20according%20to%20research%20conducted%20by%20Veris%20Insights.%20For%20some%20employers%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcant-get-job-not-your-fault-recruiters-unemployed-hiring-openings-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eleaner%20recruiting%20teams%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20also%20be%20driving%20a%20narrower%20focus%20on%20certain%20candidates%2C%20as%20some%20firms%20haven't%20rebuilt%20hiring%20teams%20to%20pre-pandemic%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20time%20period%20when%20people%20were%20predicting%20that%20everyone%20could%20just%20go%20to%20a%20bootcamp%20or%20skip%20college%2C%20and%20it's%20all%20about%20their%20innate%20talent%20or%20their%20raw%20ability%20to%20code%2C%26quot%3B%20Stabile%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20may%20still%20be%20true%20for%20some%20companies%2C%20but%20particularly%20in%20quantitative%20finance%20and%20the%20most%20sought-after%20technology%20companies%20to%20work%20for%2C%20I've%20seen%20just%20the%20opposite%20of%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20several%20years%2C%20the%20shifting%20labor%20market%20has%20raised%20questions%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fregret-spending-trust-fund-on-ivy-league-degree-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evalue%20of%20an%20elite%20diploma%3C%2Fa%3E.%20First%20came%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgreat-resignation-what-to-know-who-is-quitting-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Great%20Resignation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20when%20a%20post-pandemic%20hiring%20spree%20and%20labor%20shortages%20meant%20many%20didn't%20need%20an%20elite%20degree%20%E2%80%94%20or%20at%20times%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ibm-accenture-dell-companies-no-longer-require-college-degrees-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20degree%20at%20all%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20to%20find%20work.%20Then%20came%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flow-hire-low-fire-layoffs-employees-stuck-unemployment-job-seekers-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Great%20Freeze%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20ongoing%20hiring%20slowdown%20that%20has%20led%20some%20to%20wonder%20whether%20even%20an%20elite%20diploma%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcolumbia-student-thought-ivy-league-degree-guarantee-job-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecan%20insulate%20graduates%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20a%20tougher%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjob-market-2026-great-freeze-hiring-layoffs-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecompanies%20cautiously%20resume%20hiring%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20experts%20say%20graduates%20from%20elite%20schools%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20among%20the%20first%20snapped%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20is%20speaking%20with%20workers%20who've%20found%20themselves%20at%20a%20corporate%20crossroads%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20due%20to%20a%20layoff%2C%20resignation%2C%20job%20search%2C%20or%20shifting%20workplace%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShare%20your%20story%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSechTVqVWQve8iqYssNriCXdtwwdgGRixNNZpmslSKBQqIJ8g%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dheader%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efilling%20out%20this%20form%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20contacting%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajzinkula%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejzinkula%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20via%20Signal%20at%20jzinkula.29.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b4daa24e-9820-42e7-a29f-6feeb49faa2e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20elite%20college%20comeback%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20December%202025%2C%20the%20most%20recent%20data%20available%2C%205.6%25%20of%20recent%20college%20graduates%20ages%2022%20to%2027%20were%20unemployed%2C%20up%20from%204.8%25%20a%20year%20earlier%20and%203.9%25%20in%202022%2C%20according%20to%20an%20analysis%20by%20the%20New%20York%20Fed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20some%20elite%20universities%2C%20employment%20outcomes%20appear%20to%20be%20improving%2C%20according%20to%20graduating%20student%20surveys.%20Among%20Yale's%20undergraduate%20class%20of%202025%2C%204.6%25%20of%20graduates%20were%20still%20seeking%20employment%20six%20months%20after%20graduation%2C%20down%20from%206%25%20the%20year%20prior.%20At%20Harvard%2C%20the%20share%20of%20students%20who%20reported%20they%20would%20be%20working%20or%20in%20graduate%20or%20professional%20school%20after%20graduation%20rose%20in%202025%20from%20the%20previous%20year%2C%20from%2076%25%20to%2080.1%25%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E(others%20were%20pursuing%20alternative%20post-grad%20options%20or%20still%20figuring%20out%20their%20plans).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20been%20a%20similar%20trend%20among%20MBA%20graduates%20at%20some%20elite%20universities.%20At%20Columbia%20and%20Harvard%2C%20the%20share%20of%202025%20graduates%20who%20accepted%20job%20offers%20within%20three%20months%20of%20graduation%20rose%20from%20the%20previous%20year%2C%20from%2086%25%20to%2090%25%20at%20Columbia%20and%20from%2077%25%20to%2084%25%20at%20Harvard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20hiring%20slows%2C%20companies%20tend%20to%20become%20more%20selective%2C%20said%20Lisa%20Simon%2C%20chief%20economist%20at%20Revelio%20Labs.%20That%20dynamic%20can%20help%20graduates%20from%20elite%20schools%20find%20jobs%20in%20a%20tough%20market.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20choosing%20a%20college%2C%20Simon%20said%20prestigious%20universities%20like%20Harvard%20and%20MIT%20can%20be%20among%20the%20best%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20elite%20colleges%2C%20on%20average%2C%20are%20some%20of%20the%20best%20deals%20because%20many%20people%20don't%20pay%20the%20sticker%20price%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20people%20have%20such%20high%20incomes%20afterwards.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Simon%20said%20attending%20a%20less%20prestigious%20college%20and%20choosing%20a%20high-paying%20major%20can%20offset%20many%20of%20the%20advantages%20of%20an%20elite%20school.%20She%20added%20that%20studying%20in%20a%20large%20city%20can%20also%20help%2C%20since%20proximity%20can%20make%20it%20easier%20to%20build%20connections%20with%20employers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eb6481d2-a91c-4dba-9542-a06667bce127%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EElite%20graduates%20face%20headwinds%20%E2%80%94%20but%20still%20have%20an%20edge%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20improvement%20in%20job%20placement%20at%20some%20elite%20universities%2C%20their%20graduates%20aren't%20immune%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmba-graduates-cant-find-jobs-white-collar-hiring-slowdown-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehiring%20slowdown%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20recent%20years.%20For%20example%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewhile%20the%20previously%20cited%20Yale%20employment%20figure%20improved%20from%202024%20to%202025%2C%20it%20was%20stronger%20in%202021%2C%20when%20hiring%20was%20more%20robust%20across%20the%20US%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20going%20forward%2C%20the%20advent%20of%20AI%20has%20cast%20uncertainty%20over%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgodmother-of-ai-value-of-college-degrees-silicon-valley-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efuture%20hiring%20landscape%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20all%20degree%20holders%2C%20Stabile%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20even%20as%20some%20job%20searches%20stretch%20longer%20than%20expected%2C%20the%20prestige%20of%20an%20elite%20degree%20is%20helping%20many%20graduates%20break%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFour%20days%20after%20Palashi%20Singhal%20earned%20her%20master's%20degree%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania%20in%20May%202024%2C%20an%20email%20landed%20in%20her%20inbox%20with%20every%20job%20seeker's%20nightmare%3A%20Her%20future%20employer%2C%20a%20tech%20startup%2C%20had%20reassessed%20its%20hiring%20needs%20%E2%80%94%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fupenn-graduate-had-tech-job-rescinded-job-offer-visa-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erescinded%20her%20job%20offer%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20spirits%20dropped%20from%20100%25%20to%20negative%20100%25%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Singhal%2C%20who%20is%20in%20her%2020s%20and%20lives%20in%20Philadelphia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222159%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Palashi%20Singhal%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69aae794fd4fbd083f29a671%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221619%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPalashi%20Singhal%3Cp%3EPalashi%20Singhal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20following%20month%2C%20Singhal%20landed%20a%20full-time%20research%20analyst%20contract%20role.%20She%20said%20the%20hiring%20manager%20for%20the%20position%20was%20a%20behavioral%20scientist%20who%20had%20heard%20of%20the%20UPenn%20program%20she%20was%20a%20part%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20was%20very%20familiar%20with%20my%20degree%2C%20which%20helped%20get%20my%20resume%20up%20to%20the%20top%20of%20the%20pile%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20Singhal%20later%20transitioned%20to%20a%20full-time%20W-2%20role%20at%20an%20adtech%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20one%20big%20advantage%20of%20an%20elite%20education%20is%20familiarity%20and%20an%20alumni%20network.%20For%20job%20seekers%20without%20a%20brand-name%20degree%2C%20there%20are%20ways%20to%20form%20contacts%20and%20help%20employers%20become%20familiar%20with%20your%20work.%20Singhal's%20advice%20to%20recent%20grads%2C%20regardless%20of%20their%20school%3A%20Don't%20hold%20out%20exclusively%20for%20a%20full-time%20role.%20Part-time%20or%20contract%20work%2C%20she%20said%2C%20can%20be%20the%20foot%20in%20the%20door%20that%20leads%20to%20something%20bigger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20come%20across%20a%20really%20good%20part-time%20or%20internship%20position%2C%20just%20go%20for%20it%20and%20see%20what%20happens%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fivy-league-college-degree-graduates-job-market-hiring-harvard-yale-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772959261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a9aade1fb3fcb42648f8ec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fivy-league-college-degree-graduates-job-market-hiring-harvard-yale-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elite%20college%20grads%20aren't%20immune%20to%20the%20hiring%20slowdown%2C%20but%20as%20employers%20grow%20pickier%2C%20many%20are%20still%20first%20in%20line%20for%20new%20roles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jzinkula%40insider.com%20(Jacob%20Zinkula)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fivy-league-college-degree-graduates-job-market-hiring-harvard-yale-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20surprise%20court%20decision%20for%20millions%20of%20student-loan%20borrowers%20brings%20debt%20relief%20back%20into%20the%20picture%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227822%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22President%20Donald%20Trump%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a89595d3e2f1aef369fed4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225215%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20court%20declined%20to%20approve%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20proposed%20settlement%20to%20end%20the%20SAVE%20student-loan%20repayment%20plan.%3Cp%3EKenny%20Holston-Pool%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20court%20dismissed%20Trump's%20attempt%20to%20eliminate%20the%20SAVE%20student-loan%20repayment%20plan%20ahead%20of%20schedule.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELawmakers%20and%20advocates%20are%20urging%20the%20Education%20Department%20to%20restart%20processing%20debt%20relief%20for%20eligible%20borrowers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20SAVE%20plan%20is%20still%20on%20track%20to%20be%20phased%20out%20in%202028.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESAVE%20is%20saved%20%E2%80%94%20for%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20latest%20twist%20to%20determining%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-student-loan-repayment-plan-court-setback-trump-borrowers-settlement-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESAVE%20student-loan%20repayment%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20district%20judge%20said%20in%20a%20February%2027%20ruling%20that%20he%20would%20not%20sign%20off%20on%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20proposed%20settlement%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-officially-ends-save-plan-student-loan-borrowers-resume-payments-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eeliminate%20the%20SAVE%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20that%20Trump's%20attempt%20to%20ax%20SAVE%20before%20its%20planned%20phaseout%20in%202028%20is%20moot%2C%20and%20the%20administration%20cannot%20move%20forward%20with%20an%20accelerated%20timeline%20unless%20it%20receives%20a%20new%20court%20ruling%20or%20undergoes%20the%20lengthy%20negotiated%20rulemaking%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdvocates%20and%20Democratic%20lawmakers%20said%20that%20the%20judge's%20decision%20means%20that%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20should%20move%20forward%20with%20processing%20debt%20relief%20for%20eligible%20borrowers%20on%20SAVE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20wants%20to%20hear%20about%20the%20challenges%2C%20successes%2C%20and%20unique%20experiences%20you're%20facing%20with%20your%20student%20loans.%20Do%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%3F%20Please%20fill%20out%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flnkd.in%2FeDDHUjmJ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20form%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20we'll%20be%20in%20touch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20decision%20formally%20ends%20the%20SAVE%20injunction%20that%20has%20forced%20over%207%20million%20SAVE%20borrowers%20into%20economic%20limbo%E2%80%94pushing%20meaningful%20debt%20relief%20and%20affordable%20monthly%20payments%20out%20of%20reach%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20group%20of%20Democratic%20lawmakers%2C%20including%20Sens.%20Jeff%20Merkley%20and%20Bernie%20Sanders%2C%20wrote%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.merkley.senate.gov%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2FFinal-SAVE-Plan-Letter-3.4.26.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20a%20March%204%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20added%20that%20they're%20calling%20on%20the%20department%20%26quot%3Bto%20implement%20the%20benefits%20of%20the%20SAVE%20plan%20and%20administer%20loan%20cancellation%20for%20borrowers%20on%20the%20SAVE%20Plan%20who%20are%20eligible%20for%20such%20relief%20immediately.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Education%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20following%20the%20court's%20decision%2C%20that%20it%20was%20evaluating%20the%20ruling%20and%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20subsequent%20request%20for%20comment%20on%20what%20the%20ruling%20means%20for%20borrowers%20enrolled%20in%20SAVE.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20SAVE%20plan%20was%20created%20by%20former%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20in%202023%2C%20and%20it%20intended%20to%20give%20borrowers%20cheaper%20monthly%20payments%20with%20a%20shorter%20timeline%20to%20debt%20relief.%20Since%20the%20summer%20of%202024%2C%20the%20plan%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-blocked-student-loan-borrowers-cheaper-payments-debt-cancellation-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eblocked%20due%20to%20litigation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20Trump%20administration%20announced%20a%20proposed%20settlement%20with%20the%20state%20of%20Missouri%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20states%20seeking%20to%20block%20SAVE%20%E2%80%94%20that%20would%20eliminate%20the%20plan%20ahead%20of%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20time%2C%20borrowers%20enrolled%20in%20SAVE%20have%20been%20on%20forbearance.%20The%20Department%20of%20Education%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-biden-student-loan-interest-charges-resume-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erestarted%20interest%20charges%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20SAVE%20accounts%20in%20August%202025%20and%20encouraged%20borrowers%20to%20switch%20to%20a%20different%20income-driven%20repayment%20plan%20and%20begin%20making%20payments.%20The%20department%20also%20said%20in%20court%20updates%20that%20the%20block%20on%20SAVE%20prevented%20it%20from%20processing%20loan%20forgiveness%20for%20borrowers%20who%20reached%20their%20payment%20thresholds%20on%20any%20IDR%20plan%20after%20April%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdvocates%20said%20there's%20no%20reason%20the%20department%20cannot%20move%20ahead%20with%20processing%20that%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20only%20is%20there%20no%20legal%20barrier%20to%20delivering%20those%20rights%20through%20the%20SAVE%20plan%2C%20but%20the%20Secretary%20has%20a%20legal%20obligation%20to%20do%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20Winston%20Berkman-Breen%2C%20legal%20director%20at%20advocacy%20group%20Protect%20Borrowers%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BThe%20U.S.%20Department%20of%20Education%20must%20immediately%20identify%20borrowers%20who%20are%20eligible%20to%20have%20their%20loans%20cancelled%20under%20SAVE%20and%20instruct%20their%20student%20loan%20servicers%20to%20cancel%20those%20loans.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b672d7b5-392f-48bc-b988-5513cfda4be6%5C%22%3EWhat's%20next%20for%20student-loan%20repayment%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAttempts%20to%20block%20SAVE%20aren't%20over.%20On%20March%202%2C%20the%20state%20of%20Missouri%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.courtlistener.com%2Frecap%2Fgov.uscourts.moed.211135%2Fgov.uscourts.moed.211135.95.0.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiled%20a%20motion%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20pause%20the%20ruling%20dismissing%20the%20settlement%2C%20asking%20a%20Missouri%20district%20court%20to%20reinstate%20the%20block%20on%20the%20SAVE%20plan%20and%20prevent%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20from%20processing%20any%20debt%20relief%20through%20the%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMissouri%20said%20in%20its%20motion%20that%2C%20because%20of%20the%20ruling%2C%20borrowers%20could%20start%20applying%20for%20debt%20relief%20again%2C%20and%20pausing%20the%20ruling%20would%20allow%20the%20court%20to%20review%20the%20case%20before%20those%20applications%20begin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20short%20postponement%20will%20not%20materially%20hamper%20any%20contrary%20reliance%20interests%E2%80%94because%20the%20SAVE%20Rule%20as%20it%20has%20been%20administratively%20stayed%20or%20preliminarily%20enjoined%20for%20nearly%20two%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Missouri%20wrote%20in%20its%20motion.%20%26quot%3BThus%2C%20borrowers%20will%20not%20be%20harmed%20because%20a%20brief%20administrative%20stay%20merely%20maintains%20this%20status%20quo%20of%20their%20payment%20obligations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20borrowers%20enrolled%20in%20SAVE%20are%20permitted%20to%20stay%20on%20the%20plan%20until%20the%20summer%20of%202028%2C%20when%20Trump's%20%26quot%3Bbig%20beautiful%26quot%3B%20spending%20legislation%20calls%20for%20its%20phase-out.%20After%20that%20point%2C%20borrowers%20will%20have%20two%20options%20to%20repay%20their%20loans%3A%20a%20standard%20repayment%20plan%20and%20a%20new%20Repayment%20Assistance%20Plan%2C%20which%20has%20less%20generous%20terms%20than%20SAVE%2C%20including%20forgiveness%20after%2030%20years%20of%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20plans%20are%20set%20to%20become%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-student-loan-debt-repayment-overhaul-moves-to-next-step-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eavailable%20to%20new%20borrowers%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20July%201.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20spending%20legislation%20will%20implement%20new%20caps%20on%20borrowing%20for%20advanced%20degrees%3A%20a%20%24100%2C000%20lifetime%20cap%20for%20graduate%20students%20and%20a%20%24200%2C000%20cap%20for%20professional%20students.%20The%20department%20compiled%20a%20list%20of%2010%20programs%20that%20will%20qualify%20for%20the%20professional%20program%20designation%2C%20including%20law%20and%20dentistry.%20Advocates%20and%20lawmakers%20have%20pushed%20to%20expand%20that%20definition%20to%20include%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-student-loan-repayment-overhaul-limits-for-nurses-public-comment-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epostgraduate%20nursing%20programs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20SAVE%2C%20borrowers%20are%20awaiting%20guidance%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Education.%20Borrowers%20enrolled%20on%20the%20plan%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-blocked-student-loan-borrowers-brace-higher-monthly-payments-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20lower%20monthly%20payments%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20SAVE%20have%20been%20a%20lifeline%2C%20and%20they're%20unable%20to%20afford%20the%20anticipated%20higher%20payments%20on%20a%20different%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20bracing%20for%20an%20astronomical%20bill%2C%26quot%3B%20Brenda%20McCoy%2C%20a%2060-year-old%20SAVE%20borrower%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%20goal%20was%20to%20be%20self-sufficient.%20I%20was%20making%20the%20payments%2C%20I%20was%20being%20a%20responsible%20person%2C%20but%20it%20has%20to%20be%20something%20I%20can%20afford.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20story%20to%20share%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3A%2520asheffey%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Easheffey%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-student-debt-relief-back-on-table-court-ruling-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772959141000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a895b5fd4fbd083f29878a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-student-debt-relief-back-on-table-court-ruling-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20court%20declined%20to%20approve%20Trump's%20move%20to%20end%20the%20SAVE%20student-loan%20repayment%20plan%20ahead%20of%20schedule.%20It%20ignited%20calls%20for%20prompt%20debt%20relief.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asheffey%40businessinsider.com%20(Ayelet%20Sheffey)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-student-debt-relief-back-on-table-court-ruling-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20EV%20graveyard%3A%20All%20the%20electric%20cars%20that%20automakers%20have%20axed%20this%20year%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20black%20Hyundai%20Ioniq%206%20sedan%20is%20parked%20on%20a%20section%20of%20tar%20next%20to%20a%20large%2C%20sandy%20field.%20The%20sun%20is%20setting%20behind%20a%20faraway%20mountain%20range%2C%20and%20there%20are%20two%20twirling%20windmills.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69aa46a4d3e2f1aef36a19db%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESeveral%20EV%20models%20have%20been%20pulled%20from%20automaker's%20lineups%20in%202026.%20It%20extends%20a%20trend%20that%20stretched%20from%20September%202025.%3Cp%3EHyundai%20USA%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAutomakers%20have%20been%20reorganizing%20their%20EV%20lineups%20since%20September%202025.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELegacy%20car%20brands%20%E2%80%94%20like%20Ford%2C%20Nissan%2C%20and%20Acura%20%E2%80%94%20announced%20discontinuations%20last%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBusiness%20Insider%20compiled%20a%20list%20of%20EVs%20that%20have%20been%20killed%20or%20indefinitely%20delayed%20in%202026.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAmerican%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-ev-winter-global-sales-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEV%20sales%20are%20slumping%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20September%202025%2C%20when%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fev-tax-credit-end-what-to-know-tesla-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efederal%20%247%2C500%20tax%20credit%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20US-made%20EVs%20ended%2C%20fewer%20shoppers%20have%20chosen%20a%20battery-powered%20car%20for%20their%20next%20set%20of%20wheels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202026%2C%20EV%20sales%20fell%2053.5%25%2C%20per%20CarGurus'%20data%20shared%20with%20Business%20Insider.%20The%20figures%20exclude%20direct-to-consumer%20brands%20like%20Tesla%2C%20Rivian%2C%20and%20Lucid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarmakers%20have%20responded%20to%20the%20sales%20collapse%20with%20several%20product%20cancellations.%20Last%20year%2C%20Ford%20ended%20production%20of%20the%20F-150%20Lightning%2C%20Nissan%20axed%20the%20Ariya%2C%20Acura%20stopped%20building%20the%20ZDX%2C%20and%20Volkswagen%20paused%20the%20ID.%20Buzz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cancellations%20aren't%20a%20wholesale%20retreat%20from%20EVs.%20Each%20of%20those%20brands%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fevs-stumble-automakers-ready-cheaper-cars-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enext-generation%20EV%20models%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20pipeline%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20cheaper%2C%20longer-range%2C%20and%20faster%20charging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20shake-up%20hasn't%20stopped.%20It's%20continued%20into%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20has%20compiled%20a%20running%20list%20of%20electric%20vehicles%20discontinued%20or%20indefinitely%20delayed%20since%20January%201%2C%202026%20%E2%80%94%20a%20tally%20that%20we%20will%20keep%20updating%20as%20automakers%20continue%20tinkering%20with%20their%20EV%20road%20map.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHyundai%20Ioniq%206%20Standard%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226628%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20red%20Hyundai%20Ioniq%206%20Standard%20is%20parked%20on%20a%20showroom%20floor.%20The%20driver's%20door%20is%20open%2C%20and%20the%20handles%20are%20popped%20out.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a9ef591fb3fcb426490266%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224419%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHyundai.%20confirmed%20to%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20Standard%20model%20Ioniq%206%20is%20discontinued%20in%20the%20US.%3Cp%3ESjoerd%20van%20der%20Wal%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHyundai%20confirmed%20to%20Business%20Insider%20that%20it%20will%20stop%20selling%20the%20Korean-built%2C%20standard-range%20Ioniq%206%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20retro-styled%20sedan%20never%20matched%20the%20success%20of%20its%20crossover%20sibling%2C%20the%20Ioniq%205%20(which%20the%20company%20said%20saw%20a%20surprising%2033%25%20sales%20increase%20in%20February).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHyundai%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hyundainews.com%2Freleases%2F4718%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20%3C%2Fa%3Eit%20sold%20just%20229%20Ioniq%206%20units%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSedan%20sales%20have%20declined%20a%20lot%20over%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20and%20the%20Ioniq%206%20is%20no%20exception%2C%26quot%3B%20Sam%20Abuelsamid%2C%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20market%20research%20at%20Telemetry%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWithout%20enough%20sales%20to%20justify%20US%20production%2C%20the%20numbers%20just%20don't%20add%20up%20for%20Hyundai.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHyundai%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20import%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20high-performance%20Ioniq%206%20N%20models%20to%20the%20US%20%E2%80%94%20a%20pricier%20variant%20with%20more%20oomph%20in%20the%20electric%20motor%20and%20track-focused%20upgrades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20meantime%2C%202025%20Ioniq%206%20sedans%20continue%20to%20be%20available%20at%20dealers%20alongside%20our%20award-winning%2C%20US-assembled%20Ioniq%205%20and%20Ioniq%209%20SUVs%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20automaker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ioniq%206%20will%20still%20ship%20to%20Canadian%20dealerships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E2026%20Hyundai%20Kona%20Electric%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20silver%20Hyundai%20Kona%20electric%20is%20driving%20down%20a%20roadway.%20It's%20passing%20a%20grassy%20field%20and%20some%20blurry%20trees.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69aa48defd4fbd083f29a2d2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHyundai%20also%20paused%20imports%20for%20the%202026%20Kona%20Electric.%20It%20is%20expected%20to%20return%20next%20year.%3Cp%3EHyundai%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Hyundai%20electrified%20its%20popular%20Kona%20crossover%2C%20swapping%20the%20gas%20engine%20for%20a%20battery-powered%20drivetrain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20became%20one%20of%20the%20automaker's%20first%20mass-market%20EVs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20run%20is%20now%20on%20pause.%20Hyundai%20said%20in%20February%20that%20it%20would%20not%20ship%20the%202026%20Kona%20Electric%20from%20its%20Korean%20plants%20to%20US%20dealerships.%20Like%20the%20Ioniq%206%2C%20the%20Kona%20Electric%20remains%20available%20in%20limited%20numbers%20as%20a%202025%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20model%20could%20return%20for%20the%202027%20model%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20starting%20price%20around%20%2433%2C000%2C%20it%20was%20one%20of%20the%20cheapest%20EVs%20on%20the%20US%20market%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETesla%20Model%20S%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20red%20Tesla%20Model%20S%20is%20parked%20on%20black%20tile%20during%20a%20car%20show.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a9f1a2fd4fbd083f299d46%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETesla%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%20announced%20the%20automaker%20would%20kill%20the%20Model%20S%20-%20the%20company's%20first%20ground-up%20vehicle%20-%20this%20year.%3Cp%3EVCG%2FVCG%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Model%20S%20was%20critical%20to%20Tesla's%20historic%20ascent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20sedan%20debuted%20in%202012%2C%20it%20was%20the%20company's%20first%20ground-up%20vehicle%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20sharp%20break%20from%20the%20slow%2C%20quirky%20EVs%20that%20came%20before%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20hypercar-like%20acceleration%2C%20sleek%20body%20lines%2C%20and%20a%20tech-forward%20cabin%2C%20the%20sedan%20made%20going%20electric%20feel%20aspirational%20rather%20than%20a%20legacy%20automaker's%20compliance%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20shift%20helped%20propel%20Tesla%20into%20America's%20dominant%20EV%20automaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20despite%20its%20historic%20role%2C%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%20says%20the%20%2494%2C990%20sedan%20is%20headed%20for%20an%20%26quot%3Bhonorable%20discharge%26quot%3B%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-model-s-x-discontinued-chart-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eyears%20of%20sliding%20sales%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETesla%20Model%20X%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20light%20blue%20Tesla%20Model%20X%20is%20parked%20on%20gravel%20next%20to%20a%20sandy%20hill.%20Its%20gull-wing%20back%20doors%20are%20open.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ab2c24d3e2f1aef36a2743%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETesla%20is%20also%20ending%20production%20of%20the%20high-priced%20Model%20X%20SUV.%3Cp%3ETesla%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Model%20X%20is%20also%20going%20the%20way%20of%20the%20dodo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla's%20second%20built-from-scratch%20vehicle%20will%20end%20production%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%202026%20amid%20soft%20demand.%20The%20SUV%20starts%20at%20%2499%2C990.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELaunched%20in%202015%2C%20the%20Model%20X%20was%20ambitious.%20And%20complicated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20signature%20second-row%20falcon-wing%20doors%20%E2%80%94%20which%20opened%20by%20pivoting%20upward%20via%20electronically%20connected%20hinges%20mounted%20to%20the%20roof%20%E2%80%94%20became%20a%20production%20headache.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20once%20called%20the%20car%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-tesla-trump-should-buy-depending-what-he-wants-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EFaberg%C3%A9%20egg.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20production%20lines%20that%20made%20the%20two%20vehicles%20will%20now%20build%20the%20company's%20Optimus%20robots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20really%20moving%20into%20a%20future%20that%20is%20based%20on%20autonomy%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said%20while%20announcing%20their%20final%20days%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20decision%20was%20%26quot%3Bslightly%20sad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EKia%20EV6%20GT%2C%20EV9%20GT%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20red%20Kia%20EV6%20GT%20is%20parked%20on%20a%20showroom%20floor%20with%20the%20headlights%20on%2C%20and%20the%20driver's%20side%20doors%20open.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a9efbed3e2f1aef36a1471%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKia%20is%20also%20ending%20sales%20of%20its%20highest-powered%20EV6.%3Cp%3EDavid%20Benito%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKia%20is%20also%20tweaking%20its%20EV%20plans%20%E2%80%94%20but%20more%20narrowly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Korean%20automaker%20is%20delaying%20the%20GT%20trims%20of%20two%20models%2C%20the%20EV6%20and%20EV9.%20Those%20versions%20are%20the%20highest-performance%20variants%20in%20each%20lineup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKia%20confirmed%20to%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20GT%20trims%20are%20delayed%20%26quot%3Buntil%20further%20notice%26quot%3B%20due%20to%20%26quot%3Bchanging%20market%20conditions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20trims%20%E2%80%94%20which%20are%20made%20at%20Kia's%20plant%20in%20West%20Point%2C%20Georgia%20%E2%80%94%20remain%20on%20sale%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20delay%20does%20not%20impact%20the%20availability%20of%20other%20trims%20in%20the%20EV6%20and%20EV9%20lineups%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fevs-automakers-axed-this-year-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772958781000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69aa46a4d3e2f1aef36a19db%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fevs-automakers-axed-this-year-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22EV%20sales%20have%20slowed%20significantly.%20Business%20Insider%20compiled%20a%20list%20of%20cars%20that%20have%20been%20discontinued%20or%20delayed%20this%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bshimkus%40insider.com%20(Ben%20Shimkus)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fevs-automakers-axed-this-year-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20veterans%20say%20America's%20Middle%20East%20wars%20reveal%20about%20Iran%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223780%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20soldiers%20exit%20a%20helicopter%20during%20the%20launch%20of%20Operation%20Shir%20Pacha%20in%20Khost%20province%2C%20along%20the%20Afghan-Pakistan%20border%2C%20Nov.%2020%2C%202008.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ab2e2c1fb3fcb426491574%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222394%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20soldiers%20exit%20a%20helicopter%20during%20the%20launch%20of%20Operation%20Shir%20Pacha%20in%20Khost%20province%2C%20along%20the%20Afghan-Pakistan%20border%2C%20Nov.%2020%2C%202008.%3Cp%3EDavid%20Furst%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EVeterans%20of%20Iraq%20and%20Afghanistan%20warn%20that%20early%20battlefield%20wins%20don't%20guarantee%20long-term%20success.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDestroying%20targets%20is%20not%20the%20same%20as%20defining%20a%20political%20endgame.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWithout%20a%20clear%20plan%2C%20wars%20can%20expand%2C%20shift%20goals%2C%20and%20drag%20on.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20military%20is%20once%20again%20at%20war%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20committing%20significant%20combat%20platforms%2C%20troops%2C%20and%20munitions%20in%20a%20fight%20against%20Iran.%20Defense%20Secretary%20Pete%20Hegseth%2C%20a%20former%20Army%20National%20Guard%20major%2C%20says%20this%20time%20is%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20Iraq.%20This%20is%20not%20endless%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHegseth%2C%20who%20served%20in%20the%20Iraq%20and%20Afghanistan%20wars%2C%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20waste%20time%20or%20lives.%26quot%3B%20Veterans%20who%20have%20studied%20those%20decadeslong%20wars%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20achieving%20that%20goal%20will%20require%20a%20clear%20endgame%20for%20when%20bombing%20stops%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20sober%20understanding%20that%20early%20battlefield%20wins%20can%20still%20end%20in%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ayatollahs%20are%20horrible%2C%20and%20they%20need%20to%20go.%20This%20is%20the%20right%20thing%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Elliot%20Ackerman%2C%20a%20decorated%20Marine%20veteran%20who%20led%20infantry%20and%20special%20operations%20units%20over%20five%20tours%20in%20Iraq%20and%20Afghanistan%20and%20later%20worked%20as%20a%20CIA%20officer%20and%20White%20House%20fellow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20true%20in%20the%20same%20way%20that%20Saddam%20Hussein%20was%20horrible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Iraqi%20dictator%20the%20US%20toppled%20in%202003.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Global%20War%20on%20Terror%20was%20complicated%20and%20dragged%20on%20for%20years%2C%20Ackerman%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAnd%20all%20of%20that%20can%20happen%20here%20as%20well.%20Doesn't%20mean%20it%20will%20happen%2C%20but%20it%20can%20happen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20US%20Navy%20Super%20Hornet%20on%20aircraft%20carrier%20Abraham%20Lincoln%20readied%20for%20a%20flight%20with%20Operation%20Epic%20Fury%20on%20Wednesday.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ab4298fd4fbd083f29b410%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20US%20Navy%20Super%20Hornet%20on%20aircraft%20carrier%20Abraham%20Lincoln%20readied%20for%20a%20flight%20with%20Operation%20Epic%20Fury%20on%20Wednesday.%3Cp%3EUS%20Navy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226ca8bd18-b14a-4f7f-be09-cac1d288ce1b%5C%22%3EWhat%20went%20wrong%20in%20past%20wars%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20wars%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firaq-a-key-test-of-trumps-willingness-to-counter-iran-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIraq%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-effort-in-afghanistan-doomed-and-risks-repeat-sigar-says-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAfghanistan%3C%2Fa%3E%20began%20with%20overwhelming%20displays%20of%20American%20military%20power%20and%20rapid%20tactical%20victories%2C%20showcasing%20the%20US%20military's%20ability%20to%20devastate%20conventional%20forces%20and%20dominate%20high-intensity%20combat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Taliban%20regime%20collapsed%20within%20weeks.%20Saddam%20Hussein's%20government%20fell%20in%2021%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20American%20forces%20found%20themselves%20battling%20decentralized%20insurgencies%2C%20often%20indistinguishable%20from%20civilian%20populations.%20Despite%20surges%20in%20troop%20numbers%20and%20technological%20superiority%2C%20the%20US%20struggled%20to%20combat%20those%20non-state%20networks%20while%20trying%20to%20rebuild%20fractured%20nations.%20This%20dragged%20the%20US%20deeper%20into%20protracted%20wars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20clearly%20defining%20strategic%20objectives%20from%20the%20outset%2C%20including%20precisely%20defined%20political%20goals%2C%20US%20leaders%20could%20retroactively%20declare%20success%20based%20on%20whatever%20outcomes%20emerged%2C%20and%20they%20did%2C%20said%20Mike%20Nelson%2C%20a%20retired%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-green-berets-actually-work-according-former-special-forces-captain%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGreen%20Beret%3C%2Fa%3E%20lieutenant%20colonel%20who%20deployed%20numerous%20times%20to%20Iraq%20and%20Afghanistan%2C%20served%20in%20senior%20roles%20at%20US%20Central%20Command%2C%20and%20later%20taught%20military%20science%20at%20George%20Mason%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224320%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22This%20partially%20redacted%20image%20from%20a%20video%20provided%20by%20US%20Central%20Command%20shows%20military%20drones%20in%20Iran%20shortly%20before%20they%20were%20struck%20by%20a%20missile%20fired%20by%20US%20forces%20on%20Sunday%2C%20March%201%2C%202026.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a847091fb3fcb42648e35b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20US%20has%20targeted%20Iran's%20missile%20and%20drone%20capabilities.%3Cp%3EUS%20Central%20Command%20via%20AP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c6134a14-520e-49a0-b2bb-be5e3815d42b%5C%22%3EAn%20endgame%20matters%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHegseth%20said%20Monday%20that%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20%26quot%3Bcalled%20the%20last%2020%20years%20of%20nation-building%20wars%20dumb%2C%20and%20he's%20right.%20This%20is%20the%20opposite.%26quot%3B%20The%20mission%20in%20Iran%20is%20%26quot%3Blaser-focused.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDestroy%20Iranian%20offensive%20missiles%2C%20destroy%20Iranian%20missile%20production%2C%20destroy%20their%20navy%20and%20other%20security%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20they%20will%20never%20have%20nuclear%20weapons%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20operation%20is%20a%20clear%2C%20devastating%2C%20decisive%20mission.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EListing%20targets%20is%20not%20the%20same%20as%20defining%20political%20objectives%20%E2%80%94%20or%20outlining%20a%20strategic%20endgame%20once%20targets%20are%20destroyed%2C%20Nelson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20larger%20question%20is%20what%20leadership%20or%20security%20conditions%20would%20mark%20the%20war's%20end%2C%20he%20said.%20Without%20that%20clarity%2C%20goals%20can%20shift%20as%20the%20battlefield%20evolves%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-war-proving-ground-for-newest-us-weapons-missile-drone-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EStrike%20campaigns%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20sharply%20degrade%20an%20adversary's%20ability%20to%20wage%20war.%20But%20from%20World%20War%20II%20to%20Vietnam%20to%20Ukraine%20to%20Gaza%2C%20strike%20campaigns%20have%20rarely%20produced%20sweeping%20political%20change%20on%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENATO's%201999%20air%20war%20over%20Kosovo%20is%20an%20exception.%20But%20that%20campaign%20relied%20on%20the%20credible%20threat%20of%20a%20ground%20invasion%20and%20sustained%20diplomatic%20pressures%2C%20not%20airpower%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENelson%20pointed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-us-says-it-caught-russia-slipping-warplanes-into-libya-2020-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELibya%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20closer%20parallel%20to%20Iran%20than%20Iraq%20or%20Afghanistan.%20In%202011%2C%20as%20Libyan%20civilians%20faced%20brutal%20violence%20from%20dictator%20Muammar%20Gaddafi%2C%20the%20Obama%20administration%20launched%20an%20air%20campaign%20that%20ultimately%20led%20to%20his%20overthrow%20and%20death.%20The%20intervention%2C%20however%2C%20ushered%20in%20years%20of%20instability%20that%20persists%20today%2C%20Nelson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221637%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22President%20Donald%20Trump%20forms%20a%20fist%20and%20holds%20it%20in%20the%20air%20before%20he%20boards%20Air%20Force%20One.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a68c24fd4fbd083f296547%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221091%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETrump%20has%20said%20that%20the%20US-Israeli%20war%20with%20Iran%20could%20last%20four%20to%20five%20weeks%2C%20but%20that%20he%20was%20prepared%20for%20it%20to%20go%20on%20for%20longer.%3Cp%3EMandel%20NGAN%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229812615f-5044-44b7-9ac6-eb00b2cbac1f%5C%22%3EThe%20stakes%20in%20Iran%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20officials%20have%20described%20the%20airstrikes%20as%20a%20stunning%20tactical%20success%2C%20saying%20they%20have%20devastated%20Iranian%20military%20assets%20and%20killed%20Iran's%20Supreme%20Leader%20Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei%2C%20along%20with%20dozens%20of%20senior%20military%20leaders.%20Satellite%20imagery%20confirms%20extensive%20damage%20to%20Iranian%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsked%20Tuesday%20about%20potential%20fallout%2C%20Trump%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20worst%20case%20would%20be%20we%20do%20this%20and%20then%20somebody%20takes%20over%20who's%20as%20bad%20as%20the%20previous%20person.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20potential%20successors%20identified%20by%20the%20US%20%E2%80%94%20and%20even%20their%20backups%20%E2%80%94%20are%20now%20dead%2C%20creating%20uncertainty%20over%20who%20could%20assume%20power%20and%20negotiate%20with%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20said%20he%20expects%20the%20war%20to%20last%20%26quot%3Bfour%20to%20five%20weeks%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20has%20said%20he%20is%20willing%20to%20go%20longer%20if%20needed.%20Hegseth%20said%20that%20the%20US%20is%20in%20this%20%26quot%3Bfor%20as%20long%20as%20it%20takes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Iranian%20military%20continues%20to%20fight%20despite%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsatellite-image-show-iran-warship-smoking-airstrikes-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esignificant%20losses%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20its%20most%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-says-iran-ayatollah-khamenei-dead-after-us-israel-strikes-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esenior%20ranks%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Iran's%20foreign%20minister%20called%20the%20strategy%20a%20%26quot%3Bdecentralized%20mosaic%20defense%26quot%3B%20that%20gives%20remaining%20commanders%20autonomy%20to%20fight%20independently%20of%20top-level%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElements%20of%20that%20approach%20appear%20visible%20in%20Iran's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-missiles-multiple-countries-what-happened-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emissile%20campaign%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BToday%2C%20in%20their%20desperation%2C%20the%20enemy%20is%20unmasked%20as%20Iranian%20missiles%20and%20drones%20rained%20down%20indiscriminately%20on%20the%20hotels%2C%20airports%2C%20apartments%2C%20and%20other%20civilian%20targets%20of%20their%20neighbors%2C%26quot%3B%20Hegseth%20said%20on%20Monday.%20The%20Pentagon%20said%20those%20attacks%20have%20declined%20amid%20expanding%20US%20and%20Israeli%20strikes%20inside%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIran%20also%20has%20a%20far-reaching%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fits-been-rough-year-for-iran-and-friends-middle-east-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eproxy%20network%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20militias%20and%20terrorist%20groups%20that%20remain%20active%2C%20further%20complicating%20a%20difficult%20fight%20beyond%20the%20ballistic%20missiles%20and%20drones%20being%20launched%20into%20countries%20across%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tactical%20situation%20in%20this%20war%20is%20complex%2C%20making%20strategic-level%20decisions%20even%20more%20so.%20That%20makes%20having%20a%20plan%20for%20how%20it%20all%20ends%20essential%2C%20said%20Phil%20Klay%2C%20a%20Marine%20veteran%20of%20the%20war%20in%20Iraq%20and%20an%20award-winning%20author%20of%20books%20on%20the%20civil-military%20divide%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphil-klay-redeployment-2014-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehuman%20costs%20of%20war%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20roll%20the%20dice%20on%20warfare%2C%20you%20unleash%20chaos%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20when%20this%20sort%20of%20status%20quo%20is%20already%20pretty%20bad%2C%20it's%20easy%20to%20think%2C%20well%2C%20how%20bad%2C%20how%20much%20worse%20could%20it%20get%3F%20And%20the%20answer%20is%2C%20it%20can%20get%20unbelievably%20bad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdecadeslong-wars-hold-key-lessons-for-us-military-in-iran-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772958721000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ab4692d3e2f1aef36a2be2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdecadeslong-wars-hold-key-lessons-for-us-military-in-iran-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Veterans%20say%20the%20decadeslong%20wars%20in%20Iraq%20and%20Afghanistan%20hold%20key%20lessons%20for%20US%20military%20action%20in%20Iran.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kbaker%40insider.com%20(Kelsey%20Baker)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdecadeslong-wars-hold-key-lessons-for-us-military-in-iran-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Interstellar%2C%20Einstein%20and%20the%20strange%20elasticity%20of%20time%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772958691000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129260235%2Cimgsize-125654.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmumbai%2Finterstellar-einstein-and-the-strange-elasticity-of-time%2Farticleshow%2F129259757.cms%22