us-shifts-energy-language-amid-gulf-crisis-11185095%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20Iran-Israel%20war%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20squeezes%20global%20oil%20supply%2C%20the%20Trump%20administration%20hosted%20Latin%20American%20leaders%20and%20the%20US%20treasury%20secretary%20pivoted%20from%20a%20tone%20of%20authority%20to%20one%20of%20partnership%20-%20a%20shift%20in%20language.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Wave%20Of%20US%20Court%20Rulings%20Frees%20Indian%20Migrants%20From%20Detention%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22A%20wave%20of%20federal%20court%20rulings%20across%20the%20United%20States%20this%20week%20has%20ordered%20the%20release%20or%20bond%20hearings%20for%20at%20least%2015%20Indian%20nationals%20held%20in%20immigration%20detention.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772957360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F191htm5o_indian-migrants-us-shackledjpg_625x300_06_February_25.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwave-of-us-court-rulings-frees-indian-migrants-from-detention-11184238%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20wave%20of%20federal%20court%20rulings%20across%20the%20United%20States%20this%20week%20has%20ordered%20the%20release%20or%20bond%20hearings%20for%20at%20least%2015%20Indian%20nationals%20held%20in%20immigration%20detention.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%20strange%2C%20sleep-deprived%20week%20hobnobbing%20with%20the%20global%20elite%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aki%20Ito%20at%20Davos%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69977275e1ba468a96ac573b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJason%20Sanchez%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20started%20with%20a%20mysterious%20slack%20from%20our%20editor-in-chief%2C%20Jamie%20Heller%3A%20%3Cem%3ECan%20you%20talk%20now%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%20It%20was%20the%20kind%20of%20urgent%20message%20you%20never%20want%20to%20get%20from%20your%20boss'%20boss.%20What%20did%20I%20do%3F%20Am%20I%20in%20trouble%3F%20Is%20she%20laying%20me%20off%3F%20I%20scoured%20my%20brain%20for%20all%20the%20ways%20I'd%20probably%20disappointed%20her%20and%20the%20correspondingly%20appropriate%20ways%20I%20could%20apologize%20for%20those%20offenses.%20Then%20she%20called%20me%20to%20give%20me%20the%20news%3A%20She%20wanted%20to%20send%20me%20to%20Davos%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20known%20about%20Davos%2C%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum's%20annual%20conference%20that%20gathers%20the%20global%20elite%2C%20for%20my%20entire%2016-year%20career%20as%20a%20business%20journalist.%20As%20a%20young%20reporter%20at%20Bloomberg%2C%20I%20remember%20watching%20our%20TV%20anchors%20banter%20so%20effortlessly%20with%20CEOs%2C%20all%20in%20their%20puffy%20jackets%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20snowy%20Swiss%20mountains.%20I%20wondered%20if%20one%20day%20I%20would%20get%20to%20join%20their%20ranks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20our%20call%2C%20Jamie%20tried%20to%20warn%20me%20about%20the%20whole%20ordeal.%20I%20would%20be%20expected%20to%20take%2030%20meetings%20over%20the%20course%20of%20four%20days%20and%20mingle%20and%20write%20dispatches%2C%20and%20I%20would%20need%20to%20buy%20a%20very%20warm%20pair%20of%20snow%20boots.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20lot%20of%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20kept%20saying%2C%20but%20it%20went%20right%20over%20my%20head.%20I%20was%20already%20imagining%20all%20the%20executives%20I%20would%20run%20into%2C%20charming%20them%20so%20thoroughly%20that%20they%20would%20tell%20me%20their%20secrets%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20career.%20I%20would%20never%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Floyalty-employee-employer-job-security-broken-work-companies-bosses-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejob%20security%3C%2Fa%3E%20again.%20%3Cem%3EYes%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20I%20told%20her.%20%3Cem%3EIt%20was%20an%20honor.%3C%2Fem%3E%20I%20was%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20high%20lasted%20for%20the%20next%20several%20weeks.%20I%20browsed%20what%20must%20have%20been%20over%20100%20different%20blazers%20and%20blouses%20and%20pants%20and%20heels%20(I%20was%20going%20for%20chic-intellectual)%2C%20and%20shelled%20out%20for%20a%20brand%20new%20check-in%20suitcase%20to%20replace%20my%20old%20battered%20one.%20But%20as%20December%20rolled%20around%2C%20reality%20sank%20in.%20My%20colleague%20Dan%20DeFrancesco%2C%20our%20lead%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Finsider-today%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enewsletter%3C%2Fa%3E%20writer%20who%20attended%20last%20year%2C%20told%20me%20about%20the%20long%2C%20icy%20walks%20home.%20And%20those%20walks%20would%20take%20place%20after%20back-to-back%20meetings%20with%20executives%20from%207%3A30%20a.m.%20to%205%20p.m.%2C%20after%20which%20I'd%20attend%20a%20few%20happy%20hours%2C%20a%20dinner%2C%20and%20then%20a%20nightcap%20that%20would%20mercifully%20end%20at%2011%3A30%2C%20although%20there%20were%20still%20after-parties%20that%20would%20run%20later%20if%20I%20got%20in%20with%20the%20right%20crowds.%20Our%20internal%20meetings%20made%20it%20all%20seem%20very%20mandatory%2C%20the%20imperative%20for%20us%20to%20squeeze%20out%20every%20possible%20minute%20we%20were%20there%20to%20get%20inside%20the%20minds%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20powerful%20business%20leaders.%20Dan%20showed%20me%20his%20Fitbit%20data%20from%20the%20previous%20year%2C%20when%20he%20averaged%204.5%20hours%20of%20sleep%20a%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20business%20reporters%20would%20have%20been%20thrilled%20to%20get%20the%20assignment.%20But%20in%20the%20weeks%20before%20my%20flight%2C%20a%20terrible%20realization%20dawned%20on%20me%3A%20I%2C%20an%20introverted%20writer%20who%20likes%20warm%20weather%20and%20sleeping%2C%20had%20signed%20up%20for%20my%20own%20personal%20hell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20conference%20wouldn't%20start%20until%20Monday%20morning%2C%20January%2019.%20But%20by%20the%20time%20I%20arrived%20on%20Sunday%20via%20two%20flights%20and%20a%20train%2C%20Davos%20was%20already%20humming%20with%20titans-of-industry%20energy.%20Once%20a%20poor%2C%20remote%20village%20hidden%20in%20the%20Swiss%20Alps%2C%20Davos%20first%20became%20famous%20as%20a%20destination%20for%20tuberculosis%20patients%20in%20the%20mid-19th%20century.%20These%20days%2C%20it's%20a%20ski%20resort.%20On%20this%20sunny%20afternoon%2C%20men%20in%20suits%20and%20snow%20boots%20were%20walking%20by%20the%20train%20station%20with%20purpose.%20I%20dragged%20my%20heavy%20suitcase%20up%20a%20steep%20hill%20in%20the%20snow%2C%20and%20then%2C%20once%20I%20got%20to%20my%20apartment%2C%20up%20three%20flights%20of%20stairs.%20A%20little%20sweaty%2C%20I%20entered%20my%20humble%20studio%20for%20the%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Davos%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699773d6f8731049f3af6e44%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20vibe%20along%20the%20streets%20of%20Davos%20was%20less%20summit%20and%20more%20Disneyland%20%E2%80%94%20if%20you%20swapped%20all%20the%20kids%20for%20middle-aged%20powerbrokers.%3Cp%3EJason%20Sanchez%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%20for%20this%20one%20week%20during%20the%20conference%2C%20most%20of%20the%20locals%20clear%20out.%20They%20leave%20on%20their%20own%20vacations%20and%20make%20a%20fortune%20renting%20out%20their%20places.%20I%20unpacked%20my%20suitcase%2C%20steamed%20all%20my%20clothes%2C%20charged%20my%20devices%2C%20and%20then%20got%20ready%20for%20my%20first%20Davos%20engagement%3A%20a%20fancy%20dinner%20co-hosted%20by%20a%20CEO%20and%20a%20well-known%20founder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20all%20the%20way%20on%20the%20other%20end%20of%20Davos%2C%20so%20I%20decided%20to%20pick%20up%20my%20credentials%20at%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum's%20registration%20center%20along%20the%20way.%20The%20badge%20I%20put%20around%20my%20neck%20would%20be%20my%20ticket%20for%20the%20week%2C%20determining%20which%20buildings%2C%20rooms%2C%20and%20even%20streets%20I%20could%20and%20couldn't%20access.%20Mine%20was%20orange%2C%20signifying%20my%20status%20as%20a%20journalist%2C%20which%20in%20Davos'%20pecking%20order%20meant%20I%20was%20below%20the%20white%20badges%20issued%20to%20heads%20of%20state%20and%20CEOs%2C%20and%20the%20gray%20badges%20issued%20to%20other%20top%20executives.%20And%20yet%20even%20with%20my%20lower%20status%2C%20having%20a%20forum%20badge%20at%20all%20still%20meant%20I%20was%20inside%20an%20exclusive%20club%20of%20about%203%2C000%20attendees%20this%20year.%20An%20estimated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2Feurope%2F2025%2F01%2F16%2Fthe-insiders-guide-to-davos-world-economic-forum%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E20%2C000%20more%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20descend%20on%20Davos%20during%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20week%20without%20an%20official%20invite.%20They're%20here%20for%20the%20side%20panels%20and%20the%20parties%20and%20the%20vibes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20I%20knew%20I'd%20need%20every%20last%20bit%20of%20mental%20clarity%20I%20could%20muster%2C%20I%20had%20resolved%20not%20to%20drink%20for%20the%20week.%20But%20ahead%20of%20the%20dinner%2C%20the%20wife%20of%20one%20of%20its%20hosts%20held%20a%20soft%20launch%20of%20her%20own%20brand%20of%20a%20tequila-like%20spirit.%20She%20offered%20me%20a%20shot%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20walked%20in.%20An%20hour%20later%2C%20with%20my%20second%20drink%20in%20hand%2C%20I%20walked%20over%20to%20a%20man%20standing%20alone%2C%20and%20introduced%20myself%20as%20a%20workplace%20reporter.%20He%20happened%20to%20sit%20on%20the%20boards%20of%20multiple%20organizations%20and%20offered%20to%20clue%20me%20in%20on%20what%20he%20believed%20was%20the%20most%20underreported%20workplace%20story%20right%20now%3A%20that%20the%20employers%20he%20knew%20were%20avoiding%20hiring%2023-%20to%2030-year-olds%20because%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-employee-engagement-workplace-morale-careers-boomers-gen-x-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egeneration%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20young%20adults%20was%20unhirable.%20%3Cem%3EDon't%20name%20me%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20he%20warned.%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20already%20in%20the%20inner%20circle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222316%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aki%20Ito%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699b5972156648bc16a8ab4f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223088%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAki%20Ito%3Cp%3EAki%20Ito%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20dinner%2C%20I%20sat%20between%20two%20nonprofit%20executives%2C%20both%20of%20whom%20were%20repeat%20Davosians%20with%20mixed%20feelings%20about%20being%20there.%20One%20confessed%20Davos%20wasn't%20a%20great%20venue%20for%20fundraising%2C%20despite%20all%20the%20billionaires%20%E2%80%94%20something%20that%20made%20the%20%24100%2C000%20she%20and%20her%20colleague%20were%20paying%20for%20their%20three-bedroom%20suite%20difficult%20to%20justify.%20The%20other%20executive%20felt%20morally%20compromised.%20He%20came%20every%20year%20in%20the%20hopes%20of%20influencing%20the%20minds%20of%20business%20leaders%2C%20but%20he%20worried%20he%20was%20actually%20perpetuating%20a%20broken%20system%20by%20schmoozing%20with%20them.%20He%20was%20losing%20hope%20that%20they%20could%20be%20convinced%20to%20care%20about%20anything%20other%20than%20their%20shareholders.%20Next%20year%2C%20he%20said%2C%20he%20might%20return%20as%20a%20protester.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20so%20deep%20in%20conversation%20that%20by%20the%20time%20I%20looked%20up%2C%20I%20realized%20all%20my%20colleagues%20had%20already%20left.%20A%20giddy%20thought%20occurred%20to%20me%3A%20Had%20Davos%20turned%20me%20into%20an%20extrovert%3F%20I%20slept%20well%20that%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EWhy%20do%20the%20global%20elite%20spend%20such%20exorbitant%20sums%20for%20the%20privilege%20of%20spending%20a%20week%20in%20the%20frigid%20Alps%20during%20the%20coldest%20time%20of%20the%20year%2C%20in%20peak%20flu%20season%2C%20in%20a%20ski%20town%20that%20refuses%20to%20salt%20its%20icy%20streets%3F%20It%20would%20have%20saved%20everyone%20a%20lot%20of%20trouble%20if%20the%20forum%20had%20picked%2C%20say%2C%20Hawaii%20instead.%20It%20all%20began%20with%20Klaus%20Schwab%2C%20a%20German%20economist%20who%20started%20hosting%20the%20conference%20here%20in%201971.%20His%20goal%20was%20to%20get%20businesses%20to%20think%20a%20little%20more%20about%20generating%20long-term%20value%20for%20society%20and%20a%20little%20less%20about%20wringing%20out%20short-term%20profits%20to%20shareholders%2C%20an%20idea%20known%20as%20stakeholder%20capitalism.%20%26quot%3BWe%20can't%20continue%20with%20an%20economic%20system%20driven%20by%20selfish%20values%2C%26quot%3B%20Schwab%20later%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20a%20society%2C%20economy%2C%20and%20international%20community%20that%20is%20designed%20to%20care%20for%20all%20people%20and%20the%20entire%20planet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aki%20Ito%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69977626a645d1188189a100%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20icy%20streets%20forced%20me%20to%20walk%20like%20a%20constipated%20duck.%3Cp%3EJason%20Sanchez%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%20morning%2C%20as%20I%20walked%20down%20the%20main%20street%20that%20connects%20Davos%2C%20people%20looked%20a%20little%20cold%20but%20otherwise%20happy%20to%20be%20there.%20The%20vibe%20was%20less%20summit%20and%20more%20Disneyland%20%E2%80%94%20if%20you%20swapped%20all%20the%20kids%20for%20middle-aged%20powerbrokers%20and%20the%20rides%20for%20branded%20%26quot%3Bhouses%26quot%3B%20that%20line%20the%20Promenade.%20Normally%2C%20these%20storefronts%20are%20luxury%20watch%20retailers%20and%20souvenir%20shops%20and%20outdoor%20gear%20providers%2C%20but%20just%20for%20this%20week%2C%20they%20put%20everything%20in%20storage%20to%20make%20room%20for%20multinational%20conglomerates%20to%20set%20up%20shop.%20These%20corporate%20houses%20serve%20a%20few%20functions%3A%20to%20host%20panels%20and%20parties%3B%20to%20provide%20meeting%20rooms%20for%20executives%3B%20to%20scream%20in%20neon%20lettering%20to%20passersby%20that%20their%20companies%20are%20all%20in%20on%20AI%3B%20and%20to%20give%20out%20free%20things%20that%20have%20absolutely%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20their%20business.%20Pinterest%20House%20served%20miso%20ramen.%20Uber%20House%20stocked%20giant%20bars%20of%20premium%20chocolate.%20Meta%20House%20offered%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavos-wef-live-updates-jan-20-2026-1%3Futm_source%3Dcopy-link%26utm_medium%3Dreferral%26utm_content%3Dtopbar%23i-tried-metas-orange-hot-chocolate-it-was-delicious%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorange-flavored%20hot%20chocolate%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20but%20only%20after%20its%20patrons%20scanned%20a%20QR%20code%20that%20led%20them%20into%20a%20conversation%20with%20a%20bot%20on%20WhatsApp.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20have%20time%20to%20stop%20for%20a%20warm%20beverage%20because%20I%20had%20packed%20my%20calendar%20to%20the%20brim%20that%20day%20with%20meetings%20with%20four%20senior%20corporate%20advisors%20and%20five%20C-suite%20executives.%20All%20of%20these%20meetings%20were%20quite%20far%20from%20each%20other%2C%20and%20the%20icy%20streets%20forced%20me%20to%20walk%20like%20a%20constipated%20duck%2C%20and%20there%20were%20TSA-level%20security%20checks%20backed%20up%20by%20TSA-level%20lines%20to%20get%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20these%20places.%20Whenever%20I%20could%2C%20I%20shoved%20bites%20of%20protein%20bars%20into%20my%20mouth%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20kept%20having%20to%20empty%20my%20thermos%20at%20security%2C%20which%20meant%20I%20never%20had%20water%20on%20me.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Workday's%20Haus%20in%20Davos%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699b5a78efb52c8bd0dea1b3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223210%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWorkday's%20Haus%3Cp%3EAki%20Ito%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20every%20meeting%2C%20I%20became%20more%20depleted%20%E2%80%94%20physically%2C%20mentally%2C%20emotionally%2C%20and%2C%20towards%20the%20end%2C%20existentially%20%E2%80%94%20until%20I%20arrived%20at%20my%20last%20one-on-one%20of%20the%20day.%20It%20was%20with%20a%20CFO%20who%20also%20happened%20to%20be%20a%20fellow%20Davos%20newbie.%20We%20chatted%20about%20his%20company%20for%20a%20while%2C%20and%20then%20traded%20notes%20on%20how%20bizarre%20this%20whole%20thing%20was.%20Throughout%20his%20career%2C%20he%20told%20me%2C%20he%20had%20never%20understood%20the%20point%20of%20Davos.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20read%20the%20headlines%20and%20think%20about%20it%20as%20big%20leaders%20from%20all%20over%20the%20world%20solving%20big%20problems%20like%20global%20hunger%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%20that%20he%20was%20here%2C%20he%20got%20it.%20Because%20everyone%20of%20importance%20had%20gathered%20here%2C%20they%20could%20entertain%20their%20existing%20customers%20and%20woo%20new%20ones%20in%20one%20tiny%20town%2C%20instead%20of%20on%2030%20trips%20to%20cities%20around%20the%20world.%20The%20genius%20of%20Davos%2C%20therefore%2C%20was%20entirely%20accidental%3A%20The%20forum's%20conference%20had%20become%20a%20hyper-efficient%20vehicle%20for%20the%20stewards%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffuture-of-capitalism-series-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eglobal%20capitalism%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20do%20business%20with%20each%20other.%20%26quot%3BCompanies%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CFO%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bcome%20here%20to%20sell.%26quot%3B%20For%20this%20access%2C%20businesses%20are%20charged%20a%20hefty%20membership%20fee%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20per-person%20entrance%20fee.%20All%20in%20all%2C%20companies%20that%20send%20a%20large%20delegation%20of%20executives%20pay%20more%20than%20%241%20million%20a%20year%20to%20the%20forum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20CFO%20left%2C%20I%20typed%20out%20my%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavos-wef-live-updates-jan-19-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblog%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20day%2C%20and%20then%20forced%20myself%20to%20trek%2015%20minutes%20across%20town%20to%20attend%20a%20women's%20leadership%20reception.%20The%20room%20was%20so%20packed%20it%20looked%20as%20though%20every%20woman%20who%20had%20ever%20received%20a%20promotion%20in%20the%20history%20of%20corporations%20had%20shown%20up.%20I%20squeezed%20my%20way%20to%20the%20bar%2C%20took%20one%20sip%20of%20sparkling%20water%2C%20and%20made%20my%20way%20back%20to%20the%20entrance.%20%26quot%3BBack%20so%20soon%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20guy%20at%20the%20coat%20check%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%207%3A20%20p.m.%20I%20had%20a%20dinner%20at%208%20that%20was%20a%2045-minute%20walk%20away%2C%20with%20an%20attendee%20list%20of%20150.%20There%20was%20nothing%20in%20the%20world%20that%20could%20have%20convinced%20me%20to%20talk%20to%20one%20more%20person%20that%20night%2C%20so%20I%20walked%20back%20to%20my%20apartment.%20Too%20tired%20to%20change%2C%20I%20ate%20my%20grocery-store%20dinner%20of%20grilled%20chicken%20and%20a%20box%20of%20olives%20in%20my%20underwear.%20Then%20I%20tried%20and%20failed%20to%20fall%20asleep%20a%20hundred%20different%20times.%20I%20lay%20awake%2C%20my%20mind%20still%20racing%20from%20the%20day%2C%20my%20calves%20aching%20from%20the%2021%2C000%20steps%20I'd%20taken.%20Clearly%2C%20I%20had%20neither%20the%20mental%20fortitude%20nor%20the%20physical%20stamina%20to%20hang%20with%20the%20global%20elite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20morning%20should%20have%20been%20a%20train%20wreck%20%E2%80%94%20a%207%3A30%20a.m.%20roundtable%20I%20was%20hosting%20for%20Business%20Insider%20on%20exactly%20zero%20hours%20of%20sleep.%20This%20event%20was%20what%20I%20was%20most%20nervous%20about%20ahead%20of%20Davos%2C%20and%20I%20spent%20weeks%20preparing%20for%20it.%20I%20was%20moderating%20a%20conversation%20with%2015%20chief%20people%20officers%20and%20other%20senior%20executives%20from%20some%20of%20the%20largest%20companies%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20my%20other%20meetings%20in%20Davos%2C%20the%20roundtable%20also%20revolved%20around%20AI.%20A%20central%20theme%20was%20beginning%20to%20emerge%3A%20Companies%20just%20weren't%20seeing%20the%20big%20gains%20in%20employee%20productivity%20that%20AI%20had%20promised%2C%20and%20they%20were%20figuring%20out%20what%20came%20next.%20The%20HR%20executives%20around%20the%20table%20were%20now%20deep%20in%20the%20weeds%20of%20that%20investigation%20inside%20their%20organizations.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-hype-hasnt-changed-work-yet-bosses-employees-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhat%20drove%20adoption%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20what%20backfired%3F%20Did%20employees%20have%20the%20skills%20to%20use%20these%20new%20tools%3F%20And%20how%20do%20you%20overhaul%20the%20way%20work%20gets%20done%20inside%20teams%20to%20fully%20capitalize%20on%20AI%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20executives%20recounted%20what%20worked%20and%20what%20didn't%2C%20I%20saw%20several%20of%20them%20avidly%20taking%20notes.%20They%20nodded%20and%20laughed%20and%20groaned%20at%20one%20another's%20observations%2C%20like%20a%20group%20therapy%20session%2C%20comforted%20by%20the%20shared%20reality%20that%20they%20were%20all%20wrestling%20with%20the%20same%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20roundtable%2C%20Francine%20Katsoudas%2C%20the%20chief%20people%2C%20policy%2C%20and%20purpose%20officer%20at%20Cisco%2C%20shared%20that%20she%20had%20been%20at%20a%20dinner%20the%20previous%20night.%20Half%20the%20group%20believed%20their%20workforces%20were%20going%20to%20get%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famericas-biggest-employers-facing-great-shrinking-corporations-ai-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esmaller%20because%20of%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20other%20half%20believed%20they%20would%20get%20bigger.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20a%20reminder%20that%20it%20will%20be%20what%20we%20%3Cem%3Edesign%3C%2Fem%3E%20it%20to%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20think%20about%20Davos%20and%20the%20conversations%20we're%20having%2C%20we%20are%20at%20a%20moment%20where%20we%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20change%20just%20about%20everything%20that%20we%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aki%20Ito's%20Davos%20roundtable%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6997759af8731049f3af6e90%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAt%20a%20roundtable%20I%20led%2C%20executives%20wrestled%20with%20AI's%20impact%20on%20their%20workforces.%3Cp%3ERiana%20Daehler%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20Wednesday%2C%20I'd%20found%20my%20Davos%20groove.%20I%20discovered%20the%20free%20lunch%20buffet%20at%20the%20forum's%20media%20center%2C%20which%20meant%20I%20was%20eating%20real%20food.%20I%20learned%20to%20chug%20all%20my%20water%20before%20they%20made%20me%20pour%20it%20out%20at%20security.%20I%20was%20even%20getting%20used%20to%20the%20back-to-back%20meetings.%20If%20Davos%20were%20a%20verb%20%E2%80%94%20definition%3A%20to%20power%20through%20a%20barrage%20of%20engagements%20as%20if%20it%20were%20totally%20normal%20because%20everyone%20else%20is%20doing%20it%20%E2%80%94%20I%20was%20getting%20better%20at%20Davosing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20stranger%20perks%20of%20Davosing%20is%20running%20into%20the%20random%20celebrities%20who%20show%20up.%20This%20year%2C%20that%20list%20included%20Katy%20Perry%2C%20David%20Beckham%2C%20Jon%20Batiste%2C%20and%20Billy%20Idol.%20Matt%20Damon%20is%20a%20Davos%20regular%2C%20and%20I%20would%20have%20canceled%20pretty%20much%20any%20of%20my%20meetings%20to%20go%20see%20him%20speak.%20But%20it%20clashed%20with%20the%20roundtable%20I%20was%20moderating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERobbed%20of%20my%20Jason%20Bourne%20sighting%2C%20my%20biggest%20celebrity%20encounter%20was%20with%20the%20organizational%20psychologist%20and%20author%20Adam%20Grant.%20Which%2C%20yes%2C%20not%20quite%20a%20movie%20star%20%E2%80%94%20though%20to%20the%20Davos%20crowd%2C%20something%20akin%20to%20royalty.%20It%20was%20his%2010th%20time%20there%2C%20and%20throughout%20our%20conversation%20at%20a%20hotel%20bar%2C%20people%20kept%20interrupting%20us%20to%20say%20hi.%20His%20tone%20turned%20somber%20when%20I%20asked%20him%20what%20he%20thought%20companies%20were%20getting%20wrong%20as%20they%20deploy%20AI.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20discouraged%20and%20disturbed%20by%20how%20few%20leaders%20are%20thinking%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-chatgpt-replace-jobs-unemployment-salaries-technology-economist-daron-acemoglu-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elong-term%20implications%20of%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20jobs%2C%20and%20what%20this%20means%20for%20employment%20and%20social%20unrest%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20a%20lot%20of%20knowledge%20work%20is%20disruptable%20by%20AI%2C%20if%20a%20growing%20amount%20of%20service%20work%20is%20disruptable%20by%20AI%2C%20and%20if%20manufacturing%20work%20is%20going%20to%20be%20increasingly%20done%20by%20robots%2C%20what%20are%20we%20going%20to%20do%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20people%20are%20employable%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227644%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Matt%20Damon%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ac6fdefd4fbd083f29b9aa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225096%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMatt%20Damon%3Cp%3EFabrice%20COFFRINI%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20week%2C%20executives%20kept%20saying%20that%20AI%20hadn't%20yet%20proven%20to%20be%20as%20labor-saving%20as%20they'd%20hoped.%20Most%20of%20the%20changes%20they%20were%20discussing%20would%20take%20years.%20It%20was%20also%20clear%20that%20they%20were%20committed%20to%20bringing%20about%20this%20AI%20transformation%3B%20displacement%20was%20coming.%20What%20would%20happen%20once%20they%20succeed%3F%20I%20found%20it%20hard%20to%20get%20many%20of%20them%20to%20engage%20on%20that%20question.%20Perhaps%20they%20just%20didn't%20know.%20But%20I%20was%20skeptical%20of%20their%20pledge%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20empower%20rather%20than%20replace%20their%20employees%2C%20given%20how%20common%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-layoffs-ai-job-apocalypse-white-collar-workers-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elayoffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20become%20in%20recent%20years.%20If%20they%20were%20willing%20to%20cut%20workers%20today%2C%20what%20would%20stop%20them%20from%20cutting%20far%20more%20once%20they%20figured%20out%20how%20to%20truly%20harness%20the%20potential%20of%20AI%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20shocked%20that%20there's%20not%20more%20conversation%20about%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Grant%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20afternoon%2C%20Trump%20gave%20his%20keynote%20speech%2C%20where%20he%20promised%20not%20to%20use%20force%20in%20his%20quest%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-attended-trump-speech-davos-audience-experience-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eacquire%20Greenland%3C%2Fa%3E.%20By%20that%20evening%2C%20the%20mood%20had%20shifted.%20At%20a%20couple%20of%20the%20cocktail%20parties%20I%20attended%2C%20people%20seemed%20more%20relaxed%20%E2%80%94%20perhaps%20because%20we'd%20just%20averted%20World%20War%20III.%20One%20CFO%20told%20me%20he%20worries%20about%20his%20three%20Gen%20Z%20sons'%20dating%20lives%2C%20now%20that%20young%20people%20aren't%20meeting%20at%20work%20as%20much.%20I%20also%20spoke%20to%20a%20CRO%20who%20beamed%20as%20he%20talked%20about%20the%20conversation%20he%20just%20had%20with%20his%20pre-teen%20daughter%20on%20FaceTime.%20They%20both%20seemed%20like%20good%20dads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20team%20dinner%20at%208%20p.m.%20got%20pushed%20to%209%2C%20and%20by%20the%20time%20we%20all%20arrived%20from%20our%20various%20functions%2C%20it%20was%20past%2010.%20Over%20fondue%20and%20wine%2C%20we%20reveled%20in%20the%20realization%20that%20we%20had%20survived.%20It%20had%20been%20an%20exhausting%2C%20nerve-racking%2C%20and%20ultimately%20exhilarating%20week%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20most%20productive%20weeks%20I've%20had%20in%20a%20long%20time.%20My%20notebook%20was%20full%20of%20leads.%20A%20few%20of%20us%20writers%20shared%20the%20train%20home%20with%20our%20CEO%2C%20and%20to%20my%20surprise%2C%20I%20blurted%20out%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20come%20back%20next%20year.%20Would%20she%20put%20in%20a%20good%20word%20for%20us%20with%20our%20editor-in-chief%3F%20Yes%2C%20she%20said%2C%20laughing.%20We%20hugged%20goodbye.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Davos%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69977483f8731049f3af6e67%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAs%20Davos%20wound%20down%2C%20a%20thought%20crept%20in%3A%20If%20I%20lost%20this%20job%2C%20would%20I%20be%20able%20to%20find%20another%20one%3F%3Cp%3EJason%20Sanchez%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20walked%20back%20to%20my%20apartment%2C%20I%20started%20thinking%20about%20how%20I'd%20do%20Davos%20differently%20next%20time.%20Then%2C%20a%20different%20thought%20crept%20in%3A%20Would%20I%20even%20have%20this%20job%20in%20the%20future%3F%20If%20I%20lost%20this%20job%2C%20would%20I%20be%20able%20to%20find%20another%20one%20as%20a%20reporter%3F%20Being%20a%20journalist%20has%20been%20the%20one%20constant%20of%20my%20adult%20life%20stretching%20across%20two%20continents%2C%20four%20cities%2C%20and%2011%20apartments.%20In%20the%20darkest%20months%20of%20that%20time%2C%20when%20my%20marriage%20was%20falling%20apart%2C%20and%20in%20the%20difficult%20years%20I've%20spent%20rebuilding%20my%20life%20since%2C%20I've%20still%20had%20%3Cem%3Ethis%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20this%20job%20that%20not%20only%20puts%20a%20roof%20over%20my%20head%20but%20makes%20me%20feel%20competent%20and%20useful%2C%20like%20I%20belong%20in%20this%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20is%20leaving%20more%20and%20more%20of%20us%20wondering%20where%20our%20place%20is.%20A%20few%20weeks%20after%20Davos%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-secure-job-in-tech-block-layoffs-ai-warning-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBlock%20eliminated%3C%2Fa%3E%20nearly%20half%20its%2010%2C000-plus%20workforce.%20%26quot%3BWithin%20the%20next%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20its%20CEO%20told%20investors%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20believe%20the%20majority%20of%20companies%20will%20reach%20the%20same%20conclusion%20and%20make%20similar%20structural%20changes.%26quot%3B%20Other%20CEOs%20may%20prove%20him%20wrong%2C%20but%20the%20markets%20sent%20a%20clear%20message%3A%20Block's%20shares%20jumped%2022%25.%20It's%20not%20a%20good%20sign%20for%20the%20stakeholder%20capitalism%20that%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20was%20founded%20to%20promote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Davos%20wound%20down%2C%20I%20finished%20up%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20meetings%2C%20attended%20a%20few%20parties%2C%20and%20packed%20my%20things.%20I%20then%20began%20the%20long%20journey%20back%20to%20California%2C%20and%2021%20hours%20later%2C%20I%20was%20home.%20I%20still%20had%20a%20story%20to%20file%2C%20a%20thousand%20texts%20and%20emails%20to%20reply%20to%2C%20a%20dog%20to%20pick%20up.%20But%20for%20the%20moment%2C%20I%20was%20back%20in%20my%20own%20bed.%20I%20slept%20for%2010%20hours%20straight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Faki-ito%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EAki%20Ito%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20chief%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsleep-deprived-week-global-elite-jobs-davos-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772957221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699772d8a645d1188189a05f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsleep-deprived-week-global-elite-jobs-davos-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20spent%20a%20week%20with%20the%20global%20elite%20in%20Davos.%20There%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20talk%20about%20your%20job.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aito%40businessinsider.com%20(Aki%20Ito)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsleep-deprived-week-global-elite-jobs-davos-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Over%2052%2C000%20Indians%20fly%20home%20from%20UAE%2C%20Gulf%20within%20a%20week%20as%20authorities%20issue%20update%20amid%20US-Iran%20conflict%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772957173000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129259575