t%20Ricky%20Martin%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772955786000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129258734%2Cimgsize-693779.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fall-you-need-to-know-about-ricky-martin-the-global-icon-who-will-perform-at-the-t20-world-cup-closing-ceremony%2Fphotostory%2F129258734.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F129258734.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20T20%20World%20Cup%20final%20match%2C%20where%20India%20will%20compete%20against%20New%20Zealand%2C%20is%20set%20to%20see%20a%20global%20icon%2C%20Ricky%20Martin%2C%20perform%20at%20the%20closing%20ceremony.%20Known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98King%20of%20Latin%20Pop%2C%E2%80%99%20Martin%20is%20a%20global%20sensation%20and%20has%20won%20multiple%20Grammy%20Awards.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20everything%20to%20know%20about%20Ricky%20Martin.Ricky%20Martin%3A%20From%20Enrique%20to%20King%20of%20PopRicky%20Martin%20was%20born%20Enrique%20Mart%C3%ADn%20Morales%20on%20December%2024%2C%201971%2C%20in%20San%20Juan%2C%20Puerto%20Rico.%20He%20was%20raised%20in%20a%20large%20family%20and%20exposed%20to%20music%20and%20performance%20at%20an%20early%20age.%20As%20a%20child%2C%20he%20appeared%20in%20television%20commercials%20in%20Puerto%20Rico.The%20Puerto%20Rican%20singer%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98King%20of%20Latin%20Pop%E2%80%99%2C%20Ricky%20Martin%2C%20is%20credited%20with%20leading%20the%20%26quot%3BLatin%20explosion%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20late%201990s.%20Ricky%20has%20a%20reputation%20of%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20Spanish%20music%20to%20blend%20with%20English%20music.%20Ricky%20Martin%20is%20also%20an%20actor%20and%20author.%20Ricky%20Martin%20was%20also%20a%20guest%20performer%20at%20fellow%20Puerto%20Rican%20star%20Bad%20Bunny%E2%80%99s%20Super%20Bowl%20performance%20i