%3B%20Amodei%20said%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltman%20moved%20to%20amend%20the%20deal%20amid%20mounting%20criticism.%20It%20wasn't%20enough%20to%20quell%20the%20backlash%2C%20which%20came%20fast%20and%20threatened%20both%20OpenAI's%20reputation%20and%20its%20reign%20as%20the%20leading%20AI%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOpenAI's%20head%20of%20robotics%20quits%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221775%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22OpenAI%20logo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69acb9a21fb3fcb426491f71%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221331%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESamuel%20Boivin%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcaitlin-kalinowski-quits-openai-robotics-head-pentagon-deal-sam-altman-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECaitlin%20Kalinowski%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20hardware%20executive%20who%20joined%20OpenAI%20from%20Meta%20in%202024%20to%20lead%20its%20robotics%20division%2C%20announced%20her%20resignation%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20she%20denounced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-ai-deal-sam-altman-pentagon-defense-department-anthropic-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI's%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20Pentagon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20has%20an%20important%20role%20in%20national%20security.%20But%20surveillance%20of%20Americans%20without%20judicial%20oversight%20and%20lethal%20autonomy%20without%20human%20authorization%20are%20lines%20that%20deserved%20more%20deliberation%20than%20they%20got%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20confirmed%20Kalinowski's%20departure%20and%20defended%20the%20Defense%20Department%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20our%20agreement%20with%20the%20Pentagon%20creates%20a%20workable%20path%20for%20responsible%20national%20security%20uses%20of%20AI%20while%20making%20clear%20our%20red%20lines%3A%20no%20domestic%20surveillance%20and%20no%20autonomous%20weapons%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWe%20recognize%20that%20people%20have%20strong%20views%20about%20these%20issues%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20engage%20in%20discussion%20with%20employees%2C%20government%2C%20civil%20society%2C%20and%20communities%20around%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOpenAI%20employees%20push%20back%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228256%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22OpenAI%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69acab311fb3fcb426491f46%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENurPhoto%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20other%20OpenAI%20staffers%20have%20also%20publicly%20criticized%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-ai-deal-sam-altman-pentagon-defense-department-anthropic-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20company's%20Pentagon%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3Bi%20personally%20don't%20think%20this%20deal%20was%20worth%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Aidan%20McLaughlin%2C%20a%20research%20scientist%20at%20OpenAI%2C%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20employee%20told%20CNN%20that%20many%20of%20them%20%26quot%3Breally%20respect%26quot%3B%20Anthropic%20for%20refusing%20the%20Pentagon's%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClive%20Chan%2C%20a%20technical%20staffer%2C%20wrote%20in%20an%20X%20post%20that%20he%20believed%20OpenAI's%20contract%20barred%20the%20use%20of%20its%20models%20for%20mass%20weapons%20or%20mass%20domestic%20surveillance.%20Chan%20wrote%20that%20he's%20advocating%20for%20the%20company%20to%20share%20more%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20later%20learn%20this%20is%20not%20the%20case%2C%20then%20I%20will%20advocate%20internally%20to%20terminate%20the%20contract%2C%26quot%3B%20Chan%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20the%20deal%2C%20nearly%20900%20former%20and%20current%20OpenAI%20and%20Google%20staffers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-google-employee-petition-military-ai-use-anthropic-pentagon-defense-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esigned%20a%20joint%20petition%3C%2Fa%3E%20supporting%20Anthropic%2C%20one%20of%20their%20primary%20competitors%2C%20and%20opposing%20the%20use%20of%20their%20companies'%20technology%20for%20weapons%20that%20can%20kill%20without%20human%20oversight%20and%20mass%20surveillance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Pentagon%20is%20negotiating%20with%20Google%20and%20OpenAI%20to%20try%20to%20get%20them%20to%20agree%20to%20what%20Anthropic%20has%20refused%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20petition%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EClaude%20overtakes%20ChatGPT%20as%20consumers%20protest%20OpenAI's%20Pentagon%20deal%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225365%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20dark%20figure%20holding%20a%20phone%20with%20Claude's%20emblem%20on%20the%20screen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69acba47d3e2f1aef36a31a5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20top%20Claude%20engineer%20said%20his%20product%20is%20getting%20more%20advanced.%20He%20is%20warning%20that%20it%20could%20disrupt%20computer-based%20jobs.%3Cp%3ESamuel%20Boivin%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20deal%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclaude-number-1-app-stores-chatgpt-apple-google-ai-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eusers%20flocked%20to%20Claude%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20criticizing%20Altman's%20decision%20on%20social%20media.%20Scores%20of%20Reddit%20posts%20urged%20consumers%20to%20%26quot%3Bcancel%20ChatGPT.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUninstalls%20of%20ChatGPT%20spiked%20by%20more%20than%20295%25%20on%20February%2028%2C%20the%20day%20after%20the%20deal%20was%20announced.%20By%20Monday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-claude-hits-number-one-app-store-openai-chatgpt-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EClaude%20ranked%20No.%201%3C%2Fa%3E%20among%20the%20most%20downloaded%20free%20apps%20on%20the%20US%20Apple%20App%20Store.%20It%20remained%20in%20the%20top%20spot%20as%20of%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClaude%20is%20also%20now%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20list%20of%20most-downloaded%20productivity%20apps%20on%20the%20App%20Store.%20ChatGPT%20and%20Google's%20Gemini%20are%20close%20behind%2C%20as%20is%20xAI's%20Grok.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20also%20faced%20IRL%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EActivists%20gathered%20outside%20its%20Mission%20Bay%20headquarters%20in%20San%20Francisco%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20calling%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquitgpt-protest-against-openai-is-about-more-than-the-pentagon-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20%26quot%3BQuitGPT%26quot%3B%20movement%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Their%20anger%20with%20OpenAI%20went%20far%20beyond%20just%20the%20Pentagon%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20protesters%2C%20Sarah%20Gao%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Altman%20lived%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bsuper%20villain's%20mansion%26quot%3B%20and%20used%20his%20%26quot%3Bbillionaire%20buddies%26quot%3B%20to%20help%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20with%20%26quot%3Bhis%20disastrous%20budget%20bills%20that%20stole%20trillions%20of%20dollars%20from%20everyday%20Americans%20just%20to%20line%20their%20pockets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOpenAI's%20deal%20also%20grabbed%20lawmakers'%20attention%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226647%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20Rep.%20Sam%20Liccardo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69acaa25d3e2f1aef36a3172%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224431%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBill%20Clark%2FCQ-Roll%20Call%2C%20Inc%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20drama%20between%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-ceo-dario-amodei-pentagon-lawsuit-conversations-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnthropic%20and%20the%20Pentagon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20then%20OpenAI%2C%20California%20Democratic%20Rep.%20Sam%20Liccardo%20introduced%20an%20amendment%20to%20the%20Defense%20Production%20Act%20that%20would%20prohibit%20the%20Defense%20Department%20%26quot%3Bfrom%20retaliating%20against%20developers%20for%20instituting%20safeguards%20on%20high-risk%20technologies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20amendment%20failed%20on%20a%2016-25%20vote%20in%20the%20House%20Financial%20Services%20Committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFull%20disclosure%3A%20I%20am%20a%20Claude%20subscriber%2C%20though%20I%20can't%20claim%20to%20have%20used%20it%20to%20create%20any%20homicidal%20bots%2C%26quot%3B%20Liccardo%20said%20during%20a%20committee%20meeting.%20%26quot%3BRegardless%2C%20when%20the%20company%20that%20designs%20and%20builds%20the%20jet%20fighter%20tells%20us%20when%20to%20use%20the%20brakes%2C%20we%20should%20listen.%20Instead%2C%20the%20Pentagon's%20bureaucrats%20and%20lawyers%20believe%20they%20know%20better.%20They%20think%20they%20can%20fly%20the%20plane%20without%20brakes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDemocratic%20Sen.%20Brian%20Schatz%20of%20Hawaii%20also%20announced%20on%20X%20that%20he%20had%20%26quot%3Bdownloaded%20Claude.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAltman%20does%20damage%20control%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222368%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sam%20Altman.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69acbb8efd4fbd083f29ba53%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221776%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EFlorian%20Gaertner%2FPhotothek%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20days%20after%20the%20deal%20and%20subsequent%20backlash%2C%20Altman%20took%20steps%20to%20make%20amen