n%20in%20the%20basement.%20They%20all%20jumped%20from%20hole%20to%20hole%20to%20see%20what%20new%20miniature%20she%20had%20added%20most%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20personal%20favorites%20were%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvaluable-things-from-the-90s-worth-money-a-fortune-today%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESpice%20Girls%20dolls%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20crazy%20bones%2C%20and%20old%20playing%20cards.%20I%20loved%20the%20nostalgic%20ones%20most%2C%20the%20ones%20I%20remember%20buying%20with%20mom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20mom%20never%20stopped%20us%20from%20looking%20at%20her%20special%20finds%2C%20she%20always%20said%20that%20we%20had%20to%20look%20with%20our%20eyes%20and%20not%20touch%20with%20our%20fingers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Miniature%20collection%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a0b49ffd4fbd083f2923f2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECelina%20Myers'%20mom%20collected%20miniatures%20for%2050%20years.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Celina%20Myers%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20never%20occurred%20to%20me%20that%20her%20collection%20was%20weird.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20thought%20she%20was%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhad-chill-mom-relaxed-parent-growing-up-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereally%20cool%20mom%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20everyone%20loved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20Saturday%2C%20my%20mom%2C%20grandma%2C%20and%20I%20would%20head%20out%20to%20the%20garage%20sales%20to%20find%20new%20additions.%20We%20called%20ourselves%20the%20Three%20Musketeers.%20We'd%20scan%20all%20the%20knickknacks%20to%20see%20what%20we%20liked%2C%20what%20we%20didn't%20have%2C%20and%20what%20would%20fit%20in%20the%20typeset%20box%20compartments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMom%20also%20went%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-thrift-shop-in-every-sta