ds.%20The%20senators%20have%20previously%20called%20on%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Todd%20Spangler%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22OpenAI's%20robotics%20head%20quits%20after%20company's%20Pentagon%20deal%3A%20'This%20was%20about%20principle'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sam%20Altman%20with%20a%20finger%20to%20his%20lips%2C%20wearing%20a%20suit%20in%20front%20of%20a%20black%20and%20orange%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699cacbd2237a6a8f0cdad6b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22533%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOpenAI%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman.%3Cp%3ENathan%20Howard%E2%80%94Bloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECaitlin%20Kalinowski%2C%20OpenAI's%20head%20of%20robotics%2C%20said%20on%20Saturday%20that%20she%20had%20resigned.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20an%20X%20post%2C%20she%20criticized%20OpenAI's%20deal%20with%20the%20Pentagon.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20deal%20raised%20concerns%20over%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20surveillance%20and%20lethal%20autonomous%20systems.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECaitlin%20Kalinowski%2C%20a%20hardware%20executive%20who%20joined%20OpenAI%20from%20Meta%20in%202024%20and%20leads%20its%20robotics%20division%2C%20said%20she%20is%20resigning%20from%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Kalinowski%20criticized%20OpenAI's%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-openai-pentagon-government-deal-controversy-explained-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edeal%20with%20the%20Pentagon%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20has%20an%20important%20role%20in%20national%20security.%20But%20surveillance%20of%20Americans%20without%20judicial%20oversight%20and%20lethal%20autonomy%20without%20human%20authorization%20are%20lines%20that%20deserved%20more%20deliberation%20than%20they%20got%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20called%20her%20resignation%20a%20matter%20of%20principle%2C%20and%20said%20she%20still%20deeply%20respects%20OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20and%20is%20proud%20of%20the%20company's%20robotics%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20OpenAI%20confirmed%20Kalinowski's%20resignation%20and%20defended%20its%20deal%20with%20the%20Defense%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20our%20agreement%20with%20the%20Pentagon%20creates%20a%20workable%20path%20for%20responsible%20national%20security%20uses%20of%20AI%20while%20making%20clear%20our%20red%20lines%3A%20no%20domestic%20surveillance%20and%20no%20autonomous%20weapons%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWe%20recognize%20that%20people%20have%20strong%20views%20about%20these%20issues%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20engage%20in%20discussion%20with%20employees%2C%20government%2C%20civil%20society%2C%20and%20communities%20around%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20struck%20a%20deal%20with%20the%20Pentagon%20last%20week%2C%20allowing%20the%20Defense%20Department%20to%20use%20its%20AI%20products.%20The%20agreement%20came%20after%20its%20rival%20Anthropic%20refused%20a%20similar%20deal%20over%20concerns%20that%20the%20technology%20would%20be%20used%20for%20mass%20surveillance%20and%20autonomous%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWashington%20has%20since%20effectively%20blacklisted%20Anthropic.%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20described%20the%20company%20as%20%26quot%3Bradical%20woke%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20Truth%20Social%20post%20and%20demanded%20federal%20agencies%20stop%20using%20Anthropic's%20technology.%20Secretary%20of%20Defense%20Pete%20Hegseth%20then%20designated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-openai-pentagon-government-deal-controversy-explained-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnthropic%20a%20supply-chain%20risk%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20said%20Defense%20Department%20contractors%20would%20be%20barred%20from%20working%20with%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI's%20decision%20to%20strike%20a%20deal%20with%20the%20Pentagon%20caused%20an%20immediate%20backlash.%20Some%20users%20ditched%20ChatGPT%20in%20protest.%20Anthropic's%20chatbot%2C%20Claude%2C%20is%20now%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclaude-number-1-app-stores-chatgpt-apple-google-ai-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20No.%201%20free%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20Apple%20App%20Store%2C%20unseating%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT.%20Claude's%20US%20downloads%20increased%20240%25%20month%20over%20month%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKalinowski's%20exit%20is%20a%20setback%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopen-ai-robotics-lab-humanoid-robots-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI's%20robotics%3C%2Fa%3E%20ambitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20year%2C%20the%20company%20has%20quietly%20built%20a%20San%20Francisco%20lab%20that%20employs%20about%20100%20data%20collectors.%20Teams%20are%20training%20a%20robotic%20arm%20to%20do%20household%20chores%20as%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20push%20to%20build%20a%20humanoid%20robot.%20The%20company%20told%20employees%20in%20December%20it%20also%20plans%20to%20open%20a%20second%20lab%20in%20Richmond%2C%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20source%20with%20knowledge%20of%20OpenAI's%20plans%20also%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20company%20is%20exploring%20several%20early-stage%20hardware%20initiatives%20%E2%80%94%20including%20robotics%20%E2%80%94%20but%20none%20are%20considered%20central%20to%20its%20core%20mission%20at%20this%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcaitlin-kalinowski-quits-openai-robotics-head-pentagon-deal-sam-altman-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772905388000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ac5dd3fd4fbd083f29b952%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcaitlin-kalinowski-quits-openai-robotics-head-pentagon-deal-sam-altman-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Caitlin%20Kalinowski%20says%20she%20is%20quitting%20OpenAI%20over%20concerns%20that%20the%20technology%20could%20be%20used%20for%20mass%20surveillance%20and%20autonomous%20weapons.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lvaranasi%40businessinsider.com%20(Lakshmi%20Varanasi)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcaitlin-kalinowski-quits-openai-robotics-head-pentagon-deal-sam-altman-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nigerian%20soldiers%20'kill%2045%20bandits'%20in%20gun%20battle%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772905260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F26%2F01%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-troop-nigeria_7141517.jpg%3F20260121130529%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fnigerian-soldiers-kill-45-bandits-in-gun-battle-in-katsina-13516659%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nigeria's%20military%20has%20killed%2045%20%26quot%3Bbandits%26quot%3B%20after%20they%20allegedly%20tried%20to%20steal%20a%20herd%20of%20cattle%2C%20according%20to%20local%20officials.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fnigerian-soldiers-kill-45-bandits-in-gun-battle-in-katsina-13516659%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%20partner%20and%20I%20live%20in%20different%20homes.%20Our%20son%20moves%20between%2C%20and%20we%20each%20enjoy%20having%20time%20to%20ourselves%20each%20week.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221179%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Luana%20Ribeira%20headshot%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a0a42ffd4fbd083f2921d0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22779%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELuana%20Ribeira%20and%20her%20partner%20live%20in%20separate%20houses.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Luana%20Ribeira%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ELuana%20Ribeira%20has%20been%20with%20her%20partner%20since%202017%2C%20and%20they%20share%20a%20son.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20lived%20together%20initially%2C%20but%20moved%20into%20separate%20houses%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20says%20the%20arrangement%20allows%20each%20family%20member%20to%20have%20time%20to%20themselves.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3ELuana%20Ribeira%3Cem%3E%2C%20founder%20of%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdauntlesspr.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDauntless%20PR%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELittle%20about%20my%20relationship%20with%20Al%20is%20traditional.%20For%20starters%2C%20Al%20was%20my%20former%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-best-friend-platonic-life-partner-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehusband's%20best%20friend%3C%2Fa%3E.%20After%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20divorced%2C%20I%20moved%20to%20Portugal%2C%20where%20Al%20was%20living.%20I%20was%20planning%20on%20spending%20time%20with%20Al%20as%20a%20friend%2C%20but%20the%20second%20time%20we%20hung%20out%2C%20he%20called%20my%20ex%20to%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BThere's%20something%20here.%26quot%3B%20Luckily%2C%20my%20ex%20gave%20his%20blessing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20dating%20Al%20soon%20after%2C%20in%202017.%20In%202020%2C%20we%20moved%20to%20the%20UK%2C%20where%20I'm%20from.%20That's%20when%20we%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-been-together-for-6-years-never-slept-same-bed-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehave%20separate%20bedrooms%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20both%20were%20having%20trouble%20sleeping%20at%20the%20time%2C%20and%20enjoyed%20having%20our%20own%20space.%20We%20had%20a%20spare%20room%2C%20so%20Al%20started%20sleeping%20in%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20we%20wanted%20even%20more%20space%20from%20each%20other.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20my%20two%20teenage%20daughters%20were%20living%20with%20us%2C%20and%20the%20house%20was%20loud.%20Al%20craved%20quiet%2C%20and%20that%20was%20fine%20with%20me%20%E2%80%94%20I%20wanted%20him%20to%20take%20care%20of%20himself.%20He%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flive-small-mobile-home-independence-freedom-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econverted%20an%20existing%20warehouse%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20our%20property%20into%20a%20bedsit%20(similar%20to%20a%20studio%20apartment).%20He%20slept%20there%20and%20used%20it%20when%20he%20needed%20quiet%20time%20to%20create%20art%20or%20watch%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228147fa76-f0d6-4fb3-9e16-408a0d3f2576%5C%22%3EWe%20wanted%20different%20settings%20for%20our%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20June%2C%20we%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-florida-to-portugal-better-cost-of-living-for-family-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoved%20back%20to%20Portugal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20our%204-year-old%20son%2C%20Celyn.%20By%20that%20point%20in%20our%20relationship%2C%20Al%20and%20I%20recognized%20that%20we%20live%20completely%20opposite%20lifestyles%20at%20home.%20I%20like%20creature%20comforts%20and%20wanted%20my%20dream%20lakeside%20home%20in%20Portugal.%20Al%20was%20interested%20in%20becoming%20even%20more%20self-sufficient%2C%20living%20off-grid%20if%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAl%20already%20owned%20about%20an%20acre%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-moved-florida-southern-portugal-better-life-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eland%20in%20Portugal%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20put%20a%20yurt%20on%20the%20land%2C%20and%20now%20lives%20there%20without%20running%20water%20and%20with%20only%20limited%20solar%20power.%20The%20one%20modern%20amenity%20I%20insisted%20on%20was%20wifi%2C%20so%20I%20can%20get%20a%20hold%20of%20him%20and%20Celyn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20meanwhile%20rent%20a%20two-bedroom%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcolorado-mansion-with-100-car-garage-playboy-pool-for-sale-2019-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehome%20with%20a%20pool%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20can%20see%20a%20nearby%20lake%20from%20my%20windows.%20I'm%20still%20in%20a%20rural%20area%2C%20but%20nowhere%20near%20as%20rural%20as%20Al.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223e0714ce-2a73-4288-a86f-3d72992460b7%5C%22%3EWe%20follow%20a%20strict%20weekly%20schedule%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftips-for-coordinating-family-schedules-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehave%20a%20family%20schedule%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20might%20look%20familiar%20to%20separated%20parents%2C%20though%20Al%20and%20I%20are%20very%20much%20together.%20On%20Sunday%20nights%2C%20Al%20and%20Celyn%20go%20to%20the%20yurt.%20I%20work%20long%20days%20on%20Monday%20and%20Tuesday%2C%20and%20also%20have%20time%20to%20swim%20and%20make%20any%20appointments%20I%20need%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%20morning%2C%20I%20pick%20Celyn%20up.%20That's%20my%20favorite%20part%20of%20the%20week%2C%20seeing%20him%20run%20down%20the%20lane%20toward%20me.%20I%20have%20Celyn%20on%20my%20own%20until%20Friday%20night%2C%20when%20Al%20comes%20to%20spend%20the%20weekend%20with%20us.%20That%20family%20time%20always%20happens%20at%20my%20house%2C%20since%20it's%20more%20comfortable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdigital-detox-weekend-without-screens-helped-my-family-teen-reconnect-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eweekends%20as%20a%20family%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20sacred%20to%20us.%20It's%20also%20nice%20to%20have%20one-on-one%20time%20with%20our%20son%20and%20to%20have%20alone%20time%20built%20into%20the%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a2272499-a37d-4c8d-bdc6-efc11fa6e232%5C%22%3EThis%20arrangement%20lets%20us%20be%20ourselves%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20homes%20are%20about%2050%20minutes%20apart%20right%20now.%20If%20something%20pops%20up%20with%20work%2C%20I%20can't%20just%20send%20Celyn%20to%20his%20dad's%20on%20a%20whim.%20Sometimes%20I%20feel%20like%20I'm%20driving%20all%20the%20time%2C%20so%20I'll%20probably%20move%20closer%20to%20Al%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinancially%2C%20there's%20not%20a%20huge%20expense%20involved%20with%20having%20two%20homes.%20Al%20already%20owned%20his%20land.%20I'm%20the%20sole%20earner%20in%20our%20relationship%2C%20so%20I%20bought%20the%20yurt%2C%20and%20I%20finance%20projects%20on%20the%20land%20as%20they%20come%20up.%20Luckily%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20bills%20with%20an%20off-grid%20homestead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20this%20isn't%20for%20everyone%2C%20but%20I'm%20glad%20that%20Al%20and%20I%20can%20do%20what's%20right%20for%20us.%20We%20want%20to%20support%20each%20other%2C%20and%20don't%20want%20to%20ask%20our%20partner%20to%20change%20who%20they%20are.%20Living%20apart%20gives%20us%20the%20space%20we%20need%20to%20be%20ourselves%2C%20while%20still%20being%20a%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-living-apart-separate-homes-relationship-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772905141000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a0a4431fb3fcb426488730%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-living-apart-separate-homes-relationship-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20partner%20lives%20off-grid%20in%20a%20yurt%20while%20I%20rent%20a%20lakeside%20home.%20Living%20apart%20has%20strengthened%20our%20relationship