en%20record%20defending%20Ukraine's%20skies%20is%20headed%20to%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20Army%20is%20deploying%20the%20Merops%20system%2C%20which%20has%20scored%20over%201%2C000%20Shahed%20kills%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20propeller-driven%20interceptors%20cost%20about%20%2415%2C000%20each.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Army%20is%20deploying%20an%20American-made%20counter-drone%20system%20that%20has%20intercepted%20more%20than%201%2C000%20Shahed-type%20drones%20in%20Ukraine%20to%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20two%20defense%20officials%20confirmed%20on%20Saturday%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20US%20officials%2C%20who%20spoke%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20to%20discuss%20military%20developments%2C%20said%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnato-trying-drone-killer-proven-ukraine-against-russian-shaheds-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMerops%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20arrive%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20within%20a%20week.%20Once%20it%20arrives%2C%20it'll%20be%20ready%20for%20combat%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20declined%20to%20say%20how%20many%20systems%20the%20US%20is%20sending%20to%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20only%20that%20the%20deployment%20will%20include%20a%20large%20quantity%20of%20interceptors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Firan-drones-ukraine-russia-war-merops-75295389d8464a61d2383fb0221f4ba1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Associated%20Press%3C%2Fa%3E%20first%20reported%20the%20Merops%20deployment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20counter-drone%20system%2C%20which%20uses%20a%20roughly%20%2415%2C000%20interceptor%2C%20would%20give%20US%20and%20allied%20forces%20a%20much%20cheaper%20air%20defense%20option%20against%20Iranian%20drones%2C%20compared%20to%20expensive%20surface-to-air%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20weapon's%20deployment%20to%20the%20region%20comes%20as