nes%20like%20the%20Shahed.%20So%20far%2C%20it's%20logged%20over%201%2C000%20kills%20against%20such%20uncrewed%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Surveyor%20can%20fly%20at%20speeds%20of%20over%20175%20mph%2C%20meaning%20it's%20more%20than%20fast%20enough%20to%20catch%20Iran's%20commonly%20used%20propeller-driven%20Shahed-136%2C%20which%20flies%20at%20around%20115%20mph.%20Jet-powered%20versions%20of%20the%20Shahed%20reportedly%20fly%20as%20fast%20as%20230%20mph%20and%20are%20more%20challenging%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20Surveyor%2C%20which%20can%20be%20mounted%20with%20a%20small%20explosive%20warhead%2C%20fails%20to%20hit%20its%20target%2C%20it%20can%20deploy%20a%20parachute%20to%20allow%20retrieval%20and%20relaunch%20of%20the%20drone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223091%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Surveyor%20drone%20descends%20while%20suspended%20from%20a%20parachute.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ac5103fd4fbd083f29b90f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Surveyor%20drone%20can%20be%20retrieved%20if%20it%20fails%20to%20hit%20any%20targets.%3Cp%3EArtur%20Widak%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Business%20Insider%20observed%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-nato-next-gen-drone-killers-can-do-russia-ukraine-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edemonstration%20of%20the%20Merops%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Poland%20last%20year%2C%20one%20of%20the%20launchers%20was%20mounted%20on%20the%20back%20of%20a%20pickup%20truck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229126ee2f-43ce-4dea-8a0f-a803e6e7fab9%5C%22%3EA%20push%20for%20interceptor%20drones%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20one%20of%20the%20defense%20officials%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20with%2C%20US%20forces%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20are%20to%20be%20trained%20by%20Army%20soldiers%20from%20Europe%20to%20operate%20the%20Merops.%20The%20system%20is%20also%20being%20sent%20to%20countries%20in%20the%20region%20where%20US%20troops%20are%20not%20deployed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20defense%20official%20said%20that%20Merops'%20use%20in%20Ukraine%20has%20provided%20the%20Army%20with%20air%20defense%20information%20that%20has%20already%20proven%20valuable%20in%20Eastern%20Europe%20and%20will%20now%20be%20useful%20for%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20Army%20soldiers%20in%20Europe%20have%20taught%20NATO%20allies%20how%20to%20operate%20the%20Merops%20system%2C%20which%20was%20deployed%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-nato-next-gen-drone-killers-can-do-russia-ukraine-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ealliance's%20eastern%20flank%20%3C%2Fa%3Efollowing%20Russian%20drone%20incursions%20into%20Polish%20airspace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20said%20on%20Thursday%20that%20his%20country%20had%20received%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzelenskyy-us-support-fight-iran-shahed-drones-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edirect%20request%20from%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20help%20with%20countering%20Shahed%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZelenskyy%20shared%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Bgave%20instructions%20to%20provide%20the%20necessary%20means%20and%20ensure%20the%20presence%20of%20Ukrainian%20specialists%20who%20can%20guarantee%20the%20required%20security.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20year%2C%20Kyiv%20has%20focused%20heavily%20on%20building%20and%20deploying%20an%20arsenal%20of%20cheap%20interceptor%20drones%20to%20counter%20Russia's%20versions%20of%20the%20Shahed%2C%20which%20the%20Kremlin%20launches%20in%20hundreds-strong%20waves%20at%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukrainian-troops-air-defenses-shaheds-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUkrainian%20interceptor%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%20cost%20around%20%242%2C500%20each%2C%20and%20Zelenskyy%20has%20said%20that%20his%20country%20makes%201%2C000%20of%20them%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20these%20broader%20developments%20come%20amid%20the%20backdrop%20of%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20saying%20in%20an%20early%20morning%20TruthSocial%20post%20on%20Saturday%20that%20Iran%20had%20agreed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-damage-luxury-tourism-dubai-fairmont-palm-iran-airstrike-2026-3%23smoke-rose-over-the-palm-in-dubai-previously-a-glittering-oasis-of-calm-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estop%20attacking%20US%20allies%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIran%2C%20which%20is%20being%20beat%20to%20HELL%2C%20has%20apologized%20and%20surrendered%20to%20its%20Middle%20East%20neighbors%2C%20and%20promised%20that%20it%20will%20not%20shoot%20at%20them%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20The%20president%20also%20threatened%20additional%20action%20against%20Iran%2C%20warning%20that%20the%20US%20is%20going%20to%20hit%20it%20harder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmerops-middle-east-iran-drones-shaheds-surveyor-us-military-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772902726000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ac4ca61fb3fcb426491e1b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmerops-middle-east-iran-drones-shaheds-surveyor-us-military-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Merops%20system%20uses%20a%20roughly%20%2415%2C000%20reusable%20interceptor%20drone%2C%20giving%20the%20US%20a%20cheaper%20air%20defense%20option%20against%20Iran's%20Shahed%20drones.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jepstein%40businessinsider.com%20(Jake%20Epstein%2CMatthew%20Loh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmerops-middle-east-iran-drones-shaheds-surveyor-us-military-2026-3