.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-has-traveled-the-world-top-destinations-picks-kids-teens-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etaken%20my%20children%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%2026%20countries%20across%20six%20continents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finternational-travel-kids-stress-free-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etraveling%20with%20my%20kids%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20changed%20the%20way%20I%20parent%2C%20whether%20we're%20at%20home%20or%20thousands%20of%20miles%20away.%20Here%20are%20six%20ways%20traveling%20has%20influenced%20the%20way%20I%20parent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22966f033b-df3b-4f5e-b538-37b4d10f6e5b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20realize%20how%20little%20my%20kids%20actually%20need%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20used%20to%20be%20obsessed%20with%20getting%20my%20children%20the%20right%20type%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-stem-science-based-toys-kids-love-holiday-christmas-gift-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etoys%20to%20promote%20learning%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20development.%20I%20wondered%20if%20they%20had%20enough%20layers%20for%20playing%20in%20the%20snow%20and%20the%20best%20shoes%20for%20climbing%20at%20the%20playground.%20Through%20traveling%2C%20I%20saw%20firsthand%20how%20little%20children%20really%20need%20to%20be%20happy%20and%20thrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Marrakesh%2C%20my%20son%20played%20soccer%20in%20the%20winding%20streets%20of%20the%20ancient%20medina%20with%20kids%20wearing%20worn%2C%20off-brand%20Crocs.%20They%20barely%20stayed%20on%20their%20feet%2C%20but%20the%20game%20went%20on%2C%20full%20of%20laughter.%20In%20India%2C%20I%20saw%20children%20in%20threadbare%20clothing%20happily%20playing%20with%20no%20special%20toys%20required.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EI%20realized%20that%2C%20despite%20my%20incredible%20fortune%20to%20be%20able%20to%20get%20my%20children%20nearly%20whatever%20I%20wanted%2C%20they%20would%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuy-name-brand-clothes-for-kids-with-limited-budget-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efine%20with%20the%20basics%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20now%20know%20that%20my%20entire%20family%20is%20better%20off%20free%20from%20the%20pressures%20of%20always%20chasing%20more%20things%20and%20wanting%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2279465c49-174d-493f-a29e-82bb7e683287%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI'm%20not%20as%20hung%20up%20on%20what%20my%20children%20eat%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETravel%20often%20involves%20unexpected%20cultural%20differences%20that%20require%20my%20family%20to%20adapt%20on%20the%20fly%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20food.%20For%20breakfast%20in%20South%20Korea%2C%20we%20found%20ourselves%20with%20bowls%20of%20soup%20rather%20than%20cereal.%20In%20Egypt%2C%20we%20ate%20spaghetti%20mixed%20with%20lentils%2C%20rice%2C%20and%20chickpeas%20instead%20of%20meatballs.%20In%20Japan%2C%20our%20pizza%20came%20topped%20with%20honey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETraveling%20has%20taught%20me%20that%20many%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-went-from-having-three-picky-eaters-to-none-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efood%20rules%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20once%20accepted%20as%20gospel%20are%20really%20arbitrary%20cultural%20practices.%20I%20no%20longer%20care%20if%20my%20children%20want%20grilled%20cheese%20for%20breakfast.%20If%20they%20want%20to%20experiment%20in%20the%20kitchen%20and%20mix%20items%20that%20don't%20seem%20to%20go%20together%2C%20like%20putting%20jelly%20on%20samosas%2C%20I%20let%20them%20try%20it.%20I%20still%20care%20about%20nutrition%2C%20but%20I'm%20a%20lot%20less%20hung%20up%20on%20what%20they%20eat%20and%20when.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224618%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20poses%20with%20two%20of%20her%20children.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69aae0a21fb3fcb426490aba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20h