s%20into%20practice.%20If%20I%20have%20to%20deal%20with%20a%20last-minute%20change%20in%20plans%20because%20my%20son%20gets%20the%20flu%20or%20a%20playdate%20is%20called%20off%2C%20it's%20no%20longer%20a%20big%20deal.%20When%20I%20am%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20panic%2C%20I%20remember%20the%20time%20I%20discovered%20the%20train%20I%20had%20planned%20on%20taking%20out%20of%20Venice%20wasn't%20running.%20It%20could%20have%20been%20a%20catastrophe%2C%20but%20with%20some%20creative%20thinking%2C%20I%20got%20us%20to%20our%20next%20destination%20on%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%2C%20I%20was%20told%20(incorrectly)%20that%20my%20son%20needed%20emergency%20surgery%20in%20Jamaica.%20I%20had%20to%20make%20sure%20he%20was%20well%20cared%20for%20in%20a%20country%20with%20a%20vastly%20different%20medical%20system%20than%20the%20one%20I%20am%20used%20to.%20He%20recovered%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20with%20minimal%20intervention.%20Having%20the%20experience%20of%20navigating%20complex%20issues%20in%20countries%20where%20I%20don't%20speak%20the%20language%20and%20must%20deal%20with%20cultural%20and%20administrative%20differences%20makes%20everyday%20problems%20easier%20to%20handle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author's%20children%20hike%20along%20the%20water.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69aae0fbd3e2f1aef36a1ccb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20says%20that%20she's%20learned%20to%20let%20traditional%20schedules%20go%20and%20embrace%20being%20in%20the%20moment.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jamie%20Davis%20Smith.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cbf7861a-8b7c-44ed-859e-0c82312e4a8e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20make%20more%20time%20for%20fun%20with%20my%20children%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20role%20as%20a%20parent%20is%20often%20purely%20managerial.%20I%20drive%20my%20children%20to%20various%20activities%20and%2