help%20incentivize%20us%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20treat%20ourselves%20to%20a%20date%20after%20we%20file.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20year%2C%20since%20money%20is%20tight%2C%20our%20date%20night%20is%20a%20simple%2C%20home-cooked%20meal.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20took%20over%20four%20hours%20to%20file%20our%20taxes%20the%20first%20time%20we%20filed%20jointly.%20We%20each%20dreaded%20the%20task%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingle-adults-make-less-money-married-living-alone-rew-research-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esingle%20adults%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20together%20it%20was%20somehow%20even%20more%20unbearable.%20Not%20only%20is%20there%20more%20paperwork%20to%20submit%2C%20but%20the%20vibe%20can%20turn%20tense%20%E2%80%94%20and%20anything%20but%20romantic%20%E2%80%94%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20dealing%20with%20our%20finances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20mitigate%20this%2C%20we%20each%20gather%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ftaxes%2Fwhat-documents-do-i-need-to-file-my-taxes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etax%20documents%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20advance.%20We%20learned%20the%20hard%20way%20that%20getting%20organized%20beforehand%20cuts%20our%20time%20spent%20sitting%20at%20the%20computer%20by%20literal%20hours.%20When%20we%20each%20take%20time%20to%20gather%20what%20we%20need%20to%20file%2C%20it%20only%20takes%20us%20about%20an%20hour%20to%20file%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20finally%20hit%20%26quot%3Bsubmit%2C%26quot%3B%20we%20head%20to%20our%20yearly%20tradition%20to%20celebrate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22515ec2b6-decb-4fdd-b43c-e548833fc0b5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20hate%20doing%20our%20taxes%2C%20so%20we%20came%20up%20with%20a%20reward%20system%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20something%20to%20look%20forward%20to%20after%20filing%20really%20helps%20us%20focus%20on%20just%20getting%20it%20done%20with%20minimal%20anxiety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20few%20times%20we%20did%20our%20taxes%20this%20way%2C%20the%20reward%20was%20takeout%20from%20one%20of%20our%20favorite%20places%20and%20a%20movie%20night%20in%20with%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhate-watching-gilmore-girls-with-daughters-essay-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGilmore%20Girls%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B-%20level%20treats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20only%20our%20ideal%20date%20night%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20nostalgic%20as%20we%20started%20dating%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20All%20of%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-you-should-never-do-first-date-mistakes-etiquette-experts%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20dates%3C%2Fa%3E%20involved%20a%20nice%20takeout%20dinner%20or%20a%20movie%20night%20at%20one%20of%20our%20places%2C%20so%20our%20tax%20reward%20dates%20remind%20us%20of%20those%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224171821a-f6b0-4748-8594-c4bfd6cba012%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThis%20year%20looked%20a%20bit%20different%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20no%20longer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-manager-dresses-up-to-work-from-home-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworking%20full-time%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20health%20issues%20this%20year%2C%20and%20so%20our%20joint%20income%20has%20been%20slashed%20in%20half.%20Couple%20that%20with%20the%20rising%20cost%20of%20nearly%20everything%2C%20and%20things%20have%20gotten%20tight%20for%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20had%20to%20reexamine%20our%20budget%20periodically%20and%20cut%20costs%20where%20we%20can.%20We've%20saved%20the%20most%20money%20by%20hardly%20ever%20eating%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%20I%20wanted%20our%20reward%20to%20look%20a%20bit%20different%20this%20year.%20Instead%20of%20takeout%2C%20I%20immediately%20thought%20of%20all%20the%20things%20I%20haven't%20been%20getting%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fiamazon-fix-groceries-beat-walmart-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrocery%20store%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20we%20don't%20%26quot%3Bneed%26quot%3B%20them.%20I%20wanted%20the%20Talenti%20gelato%20I%20never%20let%20myself%20buy.%20I%20was%20also%20craving%20my%20two%20favorite%20items%20from%20the%20Publix%20bakery%3A%20guava%20pastelitos%20and%20black-and-white%20cookies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20just%20wanted%20to%20make%20his%20favorite%20comfort%20meal%3A%20tacos.%20After%20getting%20stressed%20out%20during%20the%20filing%20process%2C%20I%20think%20the%20tacos%20helped%20us%20both%20re-regulate%20afterward.%20We%20eat%20tacos%20almost%20every%20week%2C%20so%20it%20wasn't%20out%20of%20the%20norm.%20But%20I%20found%20it%20really%20interesting%20that%20after%20cutting%20back%20on%20eating%20out%20this%20year%2C%20we've%20each%20really%20grown%20to%20prefer%20our%20home%20cooking%2C%20so%20much%20so%20that%20my%20husband's%20own%20tacos%20were%20his%20reward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224b695966-16d8-482b-8336-bc690243592a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20also%20had%20to%20reframe%20the%20task%20of%20filing%20our%20taxes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20what%20our%20return%20was%20this%20year%2C%20we%20decided%20beforehand%20to%20put%20it%20toward%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurprising-things-living-in-seasonal-beach-town-all-year-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esummer%20vacation%3C%2Fa%3E%20we're%20taking%20anyway.%20This%20helped%20us%20feel%20like%20we're%20getting%20a%20%26quot%3Bfree%26quot%3B%20trip%2C%20but%20it%20also%20removes%20any%20expectation%20from%20our%20return.%20Whether%20it's%20great%20this%20year%20or%20not%2C%20looking%20at%20it%20ahead%20of%20time%20as%20a%20coupon%20for%20our%20summer%20vacation%20removes%20any%20disappointment%20if%20the%20return%20is%20awful%2C%20as%20well%20as%2