per%20acre%2C%20which%20can%20also%20go%20up%20to%20250%20quintals.%20When%20the%20rates%20are%20good%2C%20you%20can%20earn%20very%20well%20through%20this%20humble%20vegetable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20carrots%2C%20he%20also%20cultivates%20rice%20and%20maize%2C%20which%20is%20harvested%20in%20September.%20He%20claims%20to%20earn%20an%20income%20of%20Rs%201%20crore%20per%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20not%20being%20able%20to%20go%20abroad%20for%20his%20studies%2C%20he%20has%20now%20been%20able%20to%20send%20both%20his%20sons%20abroad%20for%20their%20education%20(one%20of%20whom%20has%20returned%20to%20help%20him)%2C%20bought%20a%20house%2C%20over%2030%20acres%20of%20land%2C%20along%20with%20the%20latest%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20this%20happened%20thanks%20to%20carrot%20farming.%20They%20never%20broke%20my%20heart%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhuman%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20home%20also%20doubles%20up%20as%20a%20carrot%20farming%20school%2C%20where%20he%20helps%20anyone%20interested.%20No%20young%20farmer%20is%20sent%20away%20without%20their%20questions%20being%20answered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20at%20least%20four%20farmers%20who%20come%20home%20daily%20to%20learn.%20I%20explain%20whatever%20I%20know%20in%20detail.%20I%20even%20visit%20their%20farms%20to%20teach%20them%20practically.%20I%E2%80%99m%20always%20available%20to%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20every%20aspiring%20farmer%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20lose%20hope.%20All%20you%20need%20to%20succeed%20is%20determination.%20Nothing%20is%20impossible.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EImages%20Courtesy%20Phuman%20Singh%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757233800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-30-at-11.52.18-1725875918.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D496839%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Over%20the%20past%2030%20years%2C%20Phuman%20Singh%20Kaurra%20from%20Punjab%20has%20been%20turning%20his%20family's%20fortunes%20around%20through%20carrot%20farming.%20He%20also%20has%20a%20seed%20bank%20that%20can%20cultivate%20up%20to%20650%20acres%20of%20land.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A25%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F496839%2Fpunjab-farmer-phuman-singh-carrot-farming-earns-crores%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%203%20Million%20Trees%20Brought%20Back%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20Forests%2C%20Revived%20Wildlife%20%26amp%3B%20Created%20Jobs%20for%20Thousands%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20something%20different%20in%20the%20air%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Inderjit%20Singh%2C%20a%2079-year-old%20farmer%20from%20Rajinder%20Nagar%20in%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20Fatehgarh%20Sahib%20district.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20feels%20cleaner.%20Birds%20sing%20all%20day%2C%20and%20when%20I%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F446298%2Fjunnar-family-revives-forest-digs-70-trenches-plants-450-trees%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewalk%20through%20the%20trees%20I%20planted%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20a%20forest%20that%20belongs%20to%20all%20of%20us.%E2%80%9D%20His%20voice%20carries%20the%20pride%20of%20a%20man%20who%20has%20watched%20life%20return%20to%20land%20once%20left%20barren.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20far%20from%20his%20village%2C%20in%20Lang%2C%2032-year-old%20Romanpreet%20Singh%20shares%20a%20similar%20experience.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20never%20imagined%20anything%20could%20grow%20on%20that%20patch%20of%20land%20near%20the%20crematorium.%20It%20was%20dry%20and%20forgotten.%20Now%20it%20is%20buzzing%20with%20butterflies%20and%20birds%2C%20and%20it%20has%20created%20jobs%20for%20women%20and%20youth.%20It%20brought%20our%20village%20together.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A496504%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Ftbi-showcase%2F%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20reflections%20capture%20a%20larger%20transformation%20taking%20root%20across%20rural%20Punjab.%20It%20is%20a%20movement%20of%20ecological%20renewal%20and%20communal%20healing%2C%20driven%20by%20a%20growing%20network%20of%20native%20forests%20that%20are%20reviving%20ecosystems%2C%20replenishing%20groundwater%2C%20and%20restoring%20dignity%20to%20those%20who%20care%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOne%20man%E2%80%99s%20love%20letter%20to%20Punjab%20%E2%80%93%20The%20vision%20behind%20the%20movement%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20force%20behind%20this%20change%20is%20the%20Roundglass%20Foundation%2C%20led%20by%20its%20founder%2C%20Gurpreet%20Sunny%20Singh%2C%20whose%20lifelong%20bond%20with%20Punjab%20fuels%20his%20vision%20of%20environmental%20and%20social%20renewal.%20He%20speaks%20of%20the%20land%20with%20reverence%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T195457.273_11zon-1756995925.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Billion%20Tree%20Project%20(TBTP)%20was%20started%20in%20March%202019%20to%20promote%20planting%20trees%20in%20Punjab%20villages%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T195457.273_11zon-1756995925.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T195457.273_11zon-1756995925-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T195457.273_11zon-1756995925-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T195457.273_11zon-1756995925-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T195457.273_11zon-1756995925-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496559%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Billion%20Tree%20Project%20(TBTP)%20was%20started%20in%20March%202019%20to%20promote%20planting%20trees%20in%20Punjab%20villages%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPunjab%20is%20not%20just%20a%20state%20to%20me%3B%20it%20is%20a%20breathing%20heritage.%20The%20environmental%20challenges%20we%20face%20are%20not%20isolated%3B%20they%20are%20symptoms%20of%20a%20larger%20disconnect%20between%20communities%20and%20nature.%20Our%20work%20is%20about%20restoring%20that%20bond%2C%20nurturing%20both%20land%20and%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20him%2C%20it%20is%20not%20just%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F474029%2Fjagdish-kuniyal-tree-planting-uttarakhand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplanting%20trees%20but%20about%20cultivating%20a%20future%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20nature%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20community%20grow%20in%20unison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuiding%20the%20foundation%E2%80%99s%20afforestation%20efforts%20is%20Vishal%20Chowla%2C%20project%20lead%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Billion%20Tree%20Project%20(TBTP)%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20an%20initiative%20to%20rebuild%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20green%20cover%20by%20reintroducing%20native%20tree%20species%20to%20depleted%20landscapes.%20He%20recalls%20the%20early%20days%20vividly%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20visited%20these%20villages%2C%20the%20soil%20was%20exhausted%20and%20the%20air%20heavy%20with%20pollution.%20We%20knew%20planting%20trees%20was%20essential%2C%20but%20the%20real%20challenge%20was%20to%20plant%20hope%2C%20livelihoods%2C%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20ownership%20among%20the%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20seed%20of%20hope%20was%20first%20sown%20in%20March%202019%2C%20when%20the%20foundation%20planted%20saplings%20on%20government%20land%20in%20Badaushi%20Kalan%20village.%20It%20was%20a%20modest%20start%2C%20but%20rooted%20in%20the%20idea%20of%20reviving%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20biodiversity%20with%20native%20species%20like%20desi%20beri%2C%20dhaak%2C%20phulai%2C%20and%20farah.%20These%20hardy%20trees%2C%20once%20central%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20natural%20identity%2C%20restore%20soil%20and%20water%20systems%2C%20support%20wildlife%20habitats%2C%20and%20withstand%20climate%20extremes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T200243.346_11zon-1756996410.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Roundglass%20Foundation%20encourages%20and%20educates%20the%20youth%20to%20plant%20native%20trees%20in%20their%20villages%2C%20so%20th