0alternatives%2C%20she%20says%2C%20cut%20down%20this%20carbon%20footprint%20significantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20better%20way%20forward.%20Fresh%20flowers%20end%20up%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F449690%2Fdelhi-zero-waste-colony-navjivan-vihar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egarbage%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewithin%20hours.%20Crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecan%20be%20priced%20in%20the%20same%20range%2C%20and%20you%20can%20keep%20them%20forever%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20lockdown%20hobby%20turns%20into%20forever%20memories%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%2018-year-old%20Manya%20Jain%20of%20Knot%20Kisses%2C%20the%20journey%20to%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebegan%20in%20her%20bedroom%20during%20the%202020%20lockdown.%20She%20was%20barely%2013%20when%20she%20picked%20up%20a%20hook%20because%20she%20wanted%20new%20clothes%20and%20her%20mother%20refused%20to%20buy%20them.%20What%20started%20as%20a%20rebellion%20became%20a%20craft%2C%20and%20then%20a%20calling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20taught%20myself%20entirely%20through%20YouTube%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20grandmother%20used%20to%20crochet%2C%20and%20I%20was%20always%20fascinated.%20With%20time%2C%20I%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20process.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leap%20from%20fashion%20accessories%20to%20wedding%20garlands%20came%20unexpectedly.%20At%20a%20Delhi%20event%20where%20she%20had%20set%20up%20a%20stall%2C%20a%20bride-to-be%20asked%20if%20she%20could%20make%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Efor%20her%20wedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20moment%20was%20really%20special%2C%E2%80%9D%20Manya%20smiles.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99d%20always%20imagined%20making%20one%20for%20my%20own%20wedding%20someday.%20To%20actually%20craft%20one%20for%20someone%20else%20felt%20surreal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2F